pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">1<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解决方向之一：</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">连接团队的共鸣感相似之处</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">「</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">直接谈论信任</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">」、「普通团建」</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">对信任效果不明显；</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">建议：</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">「</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">季度组织</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">情场</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">活动</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">」</span>&amp;<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">「积累信任</span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">资产</span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">」</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">重</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">大会议打造安全感的场域</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&mdash;&mdash;<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">提升「</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">沟通质量</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">」</span>&amp;<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">「决策品质」</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">路径</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">一：</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">了解</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">「</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">个人历史</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">」</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，理解</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">「</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">成员品格</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">」</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解法查看小程序中：</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">倾听人生故事」</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">路径</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">二：</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">挖掘</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">「</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">优势能力</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">」</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">和</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">「</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">资源禀赋</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">」</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解法查看小程序中：「</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">优势探寻」</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">路径</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">三：</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">提炼</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">「</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">共享的价值观</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">」</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，连接共鸣感</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解法查看小程序中：</span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">「</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">共识价值观」</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">2<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解决方向之二：</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">探索</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">和了解彼此</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">差异</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">帮助</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">「</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">消除误会</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">」、「</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">增加信任</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">」</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">重点</span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">：</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">打造「</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">安全感</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">」</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的场域，掌握</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">「</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">潜在冲突</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">」</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，帮助团队探索思维和行为上的差异。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">路径一、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">做事风格方面</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的差异</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">探索</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">具体解法：</span>Disc<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">MBTI</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\">4</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">D<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">等</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">领导</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">力测评</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">路径二、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">增加分歧和冲突的管理能力</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">具体解法</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">小程序中</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">：「分歧管理」</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、「冲突处理」</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">3<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解决方向之三：</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">营造团队积极的情绪体验</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">路径</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">一</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">团队学习</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">个体反思</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&amp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">他人积极反馈</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">具体解法</span