style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">互相推诿，前中后台矛盾多</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">发力比较分散</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">2<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解决方向</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">之一</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">优化团队</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">结构和角色</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">分工</span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">「</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">三个方向」</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">--</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">职能线分工的</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">结构特点：</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">专门的机制</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&mdash;&mdash;<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">（平衡）</span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">&rdquo;</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">协作不顺畅</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&rdquo;<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的缺点</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">--从</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">外部变化需要</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">审视</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">业务流的</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">顺畅度：保持敏感性和灵活度</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">--</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">根据</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">关键</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">任务</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的安排需要：比如专项任务小组</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">或者是横向拉通</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">机制等</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解法查看</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">「</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">清晰分工</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">」、「共识策略」</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">「管理者留意」：</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;\">--</span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">潜意识的假设，是否把</span>&ldquo;<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">结构不变</span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">当做前提</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;\">--</span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">结构和分工相关的</span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">决策</span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">&mdash;&mdash;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">属于</span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">需要团队高共识度</span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的决策类型</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">3<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解决方向</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">之二：</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">讨论</span>&ldquo;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">部门边界的和职责分配</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">；</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体-简; line-height: 21px; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体-简;\">难点：部门间</span>&ldquo;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体-简; line-height: 21px; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体-简;\">防守挡住</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体-简; line-height: 21px; font-size: 10.5pt;\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体-简; line-height: 21px; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体-简;\">，或者先推给别人。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">应对</span>&ldquo;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">部门边界的分配</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">模糊</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体-简; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体-简;\">注意：</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体-简; line-height: 21px; font-size: 10.5pt;\">1、前期&ldquo;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体-简; line-height: 21px; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体-简;\">信任</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体-简; line-height: 21px; font-size: 10.5pt;\">&rdquo;类团建的铺垫；</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体-简; line-height: 21px; font-size: 10.5pt;\">2、思想上站在</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体-简; line-height: 21px; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体-简;\">整体最优</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体-简; line-height: 21px; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体-简;\">角度探讨边界的含糊</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体-简; line-height: 21px; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体-简;\">。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">由</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">老板</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&ldquo;<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">调停</span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">&rdquo;</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">是误区，需</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">加强团队</span>&ldquo;<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">冲突应对</span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的能力</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解法查看：</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">「</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">冲突处理</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">」</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;\">二、</span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">第二类痛点</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">及解法</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;\">1、</span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">第二类痛点：</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">协作推进慢、资源共享少</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">；</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">2<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">管理者留意</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">惯性的假设</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">：</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">盯执行细节</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，可以提升</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">管控执行速度。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">影响：</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">团队</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">短视、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">割裂</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、逆反</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，反而</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">降低效率</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">3<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解决方向之一</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">两方面</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">检查信息沟通</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">顺畅</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">度</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">信息的传递</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">系统（沟通链路）</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;+&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">团队</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">有效对话</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，确保协同</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">信息</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">传递</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的顺畅</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">度</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">4<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解决方向二</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">检查</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">横向</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">部门</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">间</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">优先级</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">有无矛盾点</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解法查看：</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">「</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">左右对齐</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">」</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">5<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解决方向</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">三</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">检查</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">任务的协调复杂度是否过高。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">如果执行推动需要协调</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">一系列</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">不能直接指令的人</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、事和资源</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，需要有机制应对。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">6<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解决方向之四</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">促进成员</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">彼此间</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">能力和优势的看见</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">效果：促进</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">团队的资源共享和彼此协作。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解法查看：「共见团队资源」</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">7<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解决方式之五</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">对焦协作行动</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">避免日常执行中的摩擦。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解法查看：「行动对焦」</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">三、第三类痛点和解法</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">1<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">第三类痛点</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">团队容易有分歧</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">产生隔阂</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">沟通氛围</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">不佳</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">2<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解决方向之一：</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">与「信任三要素」有关系：</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体-简; line-height: 21px; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体-简;\">长期持续的合作关系：持续的关系让我们减少博弈，增强合作倾向性</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体-简; line-height: 21px; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体-简;\">惩恶扬善的制度安排：制度奖励滋养信任的行为，惩罚破坏信任的行为</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体-简; line-height: 21px; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体-简;\">关系的信任资产建立不足够，有分歧后容易透资关系；</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">「留意」：</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">分歧较多</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">信任</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">关键</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">资产</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">会</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">透支</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">误区：</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">直接谈论信任</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&amp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">吃饭喝酒和团建</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解法查看：</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">「</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">认可价值</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">」</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">「</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">信任版块</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">」</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 36.75pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">2<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解决方向</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">之二</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">加强团队</span>&ldquo;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">建设性的利用</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">分歧</span>&ldquo;<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">&rdquo;</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">掌控冲突</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的能力</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解法</span>1<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">：</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">判断分歧</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的焦点</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&mdash;&mdash;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-famil