span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，是</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">团队共同塑造</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">和</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">长期形成</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的。建议价值观的提取</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">方式从单向传递</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，转变成团队的</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">共同提炼</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">方式。</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">提炼来源</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">有三个方面，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">未来需要、管理层信仰、团队过去品质</span>&<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">精神</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">共同提炼的</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">效果</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，是</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">提高</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">团队</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">对结论的拥护度和认可度</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解法查看：</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">「</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">价值观共创</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">」</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">3<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解决方向之三：行为落地</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">把</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">宣传的文化词语</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，链接到团队</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">共同熟悉的情景和具体的行为</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">中。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\">     </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解法查看：</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">「</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">价值观落地</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">」</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">4<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解决方向之四：打造适合年轻员工的文化</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">用「</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">自主管理和共创</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">」的工作方式，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">整合兼顾</span> </span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">「</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"> <span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">员工诉求和激发积极性</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">」</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"> & <span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">管理层的管理需要</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解法查看：「自主管理研讨」</span></span></p>','2021-12-26 11:00:52','2021-12-31 04:44:43'),(6,'出问题总是推诿，怎么办？','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt 21pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: -21pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 21px; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">处理团队的协调，首先调整的是「处理模式」。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 21px; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">如果是「先找责任人」的处理模式，会有一些弊端，解决压力在一个人身上，所有人都不想承认我是责任方，反而加强团队的推诿。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"line-height: 21px; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"line-height: 21px; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt;\">--</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 21px; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">那不找责任，怎么解决问题呢？</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 21px; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">最重要的是关注「我们是比较新的团队，磨合的过程会出现很多问题很正常，重要的是问题能帮助团队如何成长，帮助团队如何优化合作和配合，接纳问题和愿意一起面对」。团队这样的「关注力」比归到谁身上更重要，打造一起面对问题的团队是打造文化的重点，同时要把协作不够，这类问题正常化，不是不可饶恕。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"line-height: 21px; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 21px; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">处理这个问题的「模式和方法」，首先改变的是</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;CEO</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 21px; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 21px; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">原有的假设是「有责任方才能解决问题」</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 21px; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 21px; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">改变这种模式最重要的是心底深深的认同「磨合不好很正常，打造共同面对的团队才是最重要的」。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 21px; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"line-height: 21px; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt;\">--</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 21px; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">担心其他部门会不会帮不上忙，怎么办？</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 21px; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">看上去是某一个部门的问题，但恰恰是要转换视角。不同个体的问题角度不同，部门视角是有局限性的</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 21px; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 21px; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">看问题的时候，需要更大的系统。系统上解决问题，更容易从根本上而非一个面上的点上的问题，大家的视角也可以互相的补充和提升，并且这样对齐的过程也能够让执行更加落地。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 21px; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">「每一个问题解决是一个产生凝聚力的机会」，而且是建立一个大家</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">「</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">面对</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">问题，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">共同承担</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">」</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的文化，如此大的收益背后也有代价</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">代价就是好像很多人一起在探讨他非职责之内的事情，看上去效率比较低，但这</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">正好是撬动「</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">系统改变</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">」</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">最好的办法，慢就是快。</span></span></p>','2021-12-27 00:45:18','2021-12-27 00:45:18'),(7,'没想法、没路径、没突破、执行变形等','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">一、</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">策略</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">6<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">种痛点类型</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">1<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">对用户的感知和洞察力不足、市场敏锐度不够</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">策略推进太慢</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\">2<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、对执行策略的认同度、理解度不够</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">宣讲很多遍，执行变形</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\">3<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、团队想法不够</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">老是维护性的打法</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">打法没突破</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\">4<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、策略细化没章法</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">；</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">大的容易共识，细节难落地</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\">5<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、策略模糊，容易变化，</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">重</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">点不清晰</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\">6<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、执行找理由，团队积极和努力不够</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">二、第一类痛点</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">1<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">对用户的感知和洞察力不足、市场敏锐度不够</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">策略推进太慢</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">2<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解决方向</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">：</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">转向客户满意，关注如何适应外部环境的变化</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解法查看</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\">&ldquo;洞察客户&rdquo;</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\">&ldquo;槽点改进&rdquo;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">三</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、第二类痛点</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">1<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">对执行策略的认同度、理解度不够</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">宣讲很多遍</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">执行变形</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">2<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解决方向</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">提升目标</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">认同度</span>/<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">承诺度</span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，是指</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">团队成员对目标认同，有决心克服困难的状态</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">和团队做到双向沟通</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">即使管理层已经很明确怎么做了，沟通过程着重在于用参与感加强成员的执行承诺度，并且带来更深层次的理解</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">让大部分成员愿意跟随</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解法</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">查看</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">策略共创</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&rdquo;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">四、</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">第三类痛点</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">1<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">团队想法不够，老是维护性的打法</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">打法</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">没突破</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">2<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">管理者</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">留意</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">：</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">团队</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">有没有</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">：</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">过度依赖</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">某些</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">同事</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">思维的惯性</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、很少</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">激发团队的创造力。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;\">3、</span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解决思路</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">第一、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">着重于帮助团队打破目前</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">思维惯性、局限性，帮助策略突破。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解法请查看</span>&ldquo;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">问题解决</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&rdquo;<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">&ldquo;</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">策略共创</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">第二、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">提高</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">团队</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">学习的能力</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">有效的复盘能力让策略有误及时地改进和纠偏。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解法请查看</span>&ldquo;<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">复盘改进</span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">&rdquo;</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">五、</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">第四类痛点：</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">1<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">策略细化没章法</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">大的容易共识</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">细节难落地</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;\">2、</span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解决思路</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">第一、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">向下分解时</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">创建跨职能的关键行动和配合事项</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解法查看</span>&rdquo;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">上下对齐</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">和</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">左右对齐</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">第二、对任务提供系统的落地支持，包括</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">财务、人力、激励、信息等系统的支撑</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解法查看</span>&ldquo;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">策略落地</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&rdquo;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">六、</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">第五类痛点：</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">1<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">团队策略不聚焦，容易变化，重点不清晰</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">2<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">管理者留意：</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">不同利益相关者的需求整合度，如前中后台，核心股东间；</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">诉求有冲突，容易体现不聚焦和打法模糊。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">3<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解决思路：</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解法查看</span>&ldquo;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">对齐利益相关的诉求</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&rdquo;<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">&ldquo;</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">分歧</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">管理</span>&rdquo;<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">七、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">第</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">六</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">类痛点</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">1<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">执行找理由，团队积极</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">和</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">努力</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">不够</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">2<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">管理者留意</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">彼此</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">对话</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">：对方一直处在</span>&ldquo;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">说明理由</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">和辩护</span>&rdquo;<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的状态</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">这种情形，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">通过讲道理和说教是无法解题的</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，处于</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">对抗</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的沟通，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">既无效</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">又</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">伤害彼此的</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">关系和信任，只会恶化</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">团队成员不努力的</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">状态</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">3<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解决方向</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">管理者只要</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">意识</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">到这种对抗和割裂的状态</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，改变</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">就开始发现</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。彼此尊重</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">和有信任的沟通</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，帮助</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">团队</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">更深入地交流，形成既不怕冲突又能包容差异化的团队。</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">信任</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">包含</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">长期持续的合作</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">关系，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">持续的关系让</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">团队</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">减少博弈，增强合作倾向性</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解法查看</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\">&ldquo;信任&rdquo;版块</span></p>','2021-12-31 04:58:45','2021-12-31 05:07:40'),(8,'如何对齐目标理解，上下同频','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">一、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">对齐</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\">4<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">种痛点类型</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\">1<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、方向理解对不齐</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">宣讲沉默，不知道理解认同程度</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\">2<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、市场反应尺寸，市场理解跟不上</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\">3<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、关注内部你对我错</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">不同视角巨大差异沮丧</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\">4<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、方向说多遍</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">执行变形</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">二、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">对齐方向之一：对齐外部信号</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">1<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">三种市场信号：客户、竞品、环境</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">帮助</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">团队</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">：深度理解目标策略</span> +  <span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">团队保持外部敏锐度</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">；</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">2<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">三种解决思路</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解法查看</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">「</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">对齐外部信号</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">/</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">对齐客户洞察</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">/</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">对齐竞品洞察</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">」</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">三、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">对齐方向之二：对齐内外部理解</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">1<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">目标事宜性</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">是指</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">外部需要（机会）、团队想要（热情）、能力能要（优势），</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">具体</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">三者交集</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">团队</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">通过这三个维度，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">参与</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">到</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">目标分析的研讨</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">提高认同和理解度</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解法查看</span>:</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">「</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">目标共创</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">宣讲对齐</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">」</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">四、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">对齐方向之三：对齐利益相关者诉求</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">1<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、使用情景：</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">讨论策略打法之前</span> </span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，或</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">评估任务进展好快</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">时；</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">效果</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">可以</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">增加</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">团队</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">合力</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，帮助</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">拉齐</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">任务</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">理解</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解法查看</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">「</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">对齐利益相关者诉求、复盘改进</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">」</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">五、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">对齐方向之四：上下对齐</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">1<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">通常：</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">定大目标</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">之后，进行</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">层层分解会</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">容易：讨价还价、有异议不表达</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">2<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">建议：</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">有</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">初步想法</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，先进行</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">双向沟通会</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">帮助认同度和理解度提升，再</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">定大目标</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">和分解。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">效果：</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">团队</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">更愿意理解跟随</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，并</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">共识市场基本判断、搜集信号</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解法查看：</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">「</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">目标共振</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">/<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">对齐」</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">六、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">对齐方向之四：左右对齐</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">1<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">通常</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">：</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">大目标</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">确定后，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">横向</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">部门</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">拆解</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">并</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">共晒</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。有可能忽略</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">：不同视角的优先级</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">有冲突，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">整体无法最优</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">2<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">建议：</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">大</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">目标确定后，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">策略和关键行动</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">共识，再根据关键行动和</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">配合事项</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">设定协作</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">机制</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，并</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">识别横向优先级</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">是否有</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">冲突</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解法查看：</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">「</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">左右对齐</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">」</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-right: 0.0000pt; margin-left: 0.0000pt; mso-para-margin-right: 0.0000gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0.0000gd; text-indent: 0.0000pt; mso-char-indent-count: 0.0000; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; mso-pagination: none; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\" align=\"justify\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;\">七、</span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">对齐的重要管理者心智：</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">1<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">管理者留意：无意识</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">出现</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">担心和不允许出现不同声音</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，这种</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">单边控制</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">容易让对齐会议</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">走形式、听不到真实声音</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">2.</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">打开姿态：</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">接纳</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">差异化和不同声音</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，如果当做是反调容易说服对方并觉得是噪音，如果</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">是</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">当</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">信号和视角补充</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，多一份耐心，就会愿意倾听背后的考虑。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-right: 0.0000pt; margin-left: 0.0000pt; mso-para-margin-right: 0.0000gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0.0000gd; text-indent: 0.0000pt; mso-char-indent-count: 0.0000; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; mso-pagination: none; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo2;\" align=\"justify\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;\">3、</span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">聆听和开放</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，让管理者的姿态不同，愿意让团队</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">观点表达和倾听</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">想法，这样的倾听和参与感，会让团队</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">认同和跟随</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，并</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">增加执行承诺度</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">对齐的本质，也是通过不同维度的的深度沟通，减少理解的差异，实现深层次的共识。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\">        </span></p>','2021-12-31 05:28:16','2021-12-31 05:31:32'),(9,'成长跟不上发展，培训没效果，怎么办','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;\">一、</span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">成长类痛点</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">1<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">普遍存在</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">“</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">团队学习意愿难激发，培训了却看不见</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">效果</span>”</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">将这种</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">“</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">不满意的状态</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">”</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，重构一个话题，转变为：对想提高的某类成员，在</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">学习</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">形式、</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">学习</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">时机和</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">学习</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">内容</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">方面，如何</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">恰当组合。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-right: 0.0000pt; mso-para-margin-right: 0.0000gd; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; mso-pagination: none; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l4 level1 lfo2;\" align=\"justify\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;\">2、</span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">三类痛点</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">第一、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">团队作战能力没变化</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">成长跟不上业务发展。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">第二、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">管理者能力提升，如何跟得上业务成长。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">第三、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\">CEO <span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">常常提及：管理层心态、思维、和格局不够</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">二、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">第一类痛点</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">：</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">1<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">团队作战能力没变化</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">成长</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">跟不上业务发展。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">2<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">有二种情形</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">第一、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">外部变化</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">原有工作方式，跟不上</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">变化；</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解决思路</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">：重点</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">在</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">”<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">外部适应</span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">“ &  “</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">转变的阻力</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">”</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">第二、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">规模化复制的阶段，业务能力</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">复制速度</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">能跟上</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">；</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">三类解决思路</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">：查看</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">「</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">经营复盘</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">经验萃取</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">挑战互助</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">」</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">三、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">第二类痛点</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">：</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">1<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">管理</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">者</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">能力</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">提升，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">如何跟得上业务</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">成长。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">2<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解决思路：</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">第一、</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">传统的管理者能力提升，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">指的是定方向，搭团队</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">计划协调</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">资源管理等等。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">第二、</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">针对</span>“</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">面向未来型的创业管理者</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">”</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">提出三点</span>“</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">关键能力</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">”</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">：</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">个人反思力、激发式沟通力、边界拓展力</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-right: 0.0000pt; margin-left: 21.0000pt; mso-para-margin-right: 0.0000gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0.0000gd; text-indent: -21.0000pt; mso-char-indent-count: 0.0000; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; mso-pagination: none; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo3;\" align=\"justify\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Wingdings; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;\">Ø </span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">个人反思力</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">是指，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">复杂的情形下，觉察和调整</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">自己</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的能力。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">效果：提升</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">思维</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">心态和格局</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，帮助</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">情绪管理等等。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解法查看</span>“<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">个人复盘</span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">”</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-right: 0.0000pt; margin-left: 21.0000pt; mso-para-margin-right: 0.0000gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0.0000gd; text-indent: -21.0000pt; mso-char-indent-count: 0.0000; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; mso-pagination: none; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l2 level1 lfo4;\" align=\"justify\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Wingdings; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;\">Ø </span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">激发式沟通力</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">面相未来</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">创新型</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">业务场景</span>&</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">年轻员工</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">沟通场景</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解法查看</span>“<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">沟通升级</span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">”</span></s