span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">四、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">第三类痛点</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">1<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\">CEO <span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">常常提及</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">：</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">管理层心态</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">思维</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、和</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">格局不够</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">2<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解决方向</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，用</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">团队学习</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">”<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的路径</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">效果：</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">快速提升</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">团队</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">协作力、沟通质量</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">和效率</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">第一、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">管理团队的沟通阻碍</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">做法：</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">建立相应的规则，</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">管理沟通的损耗，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">是提升团队绩效最快捷的方式。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解法查看</span>“<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">沟通阻碍管理</span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">”</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">第二、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">换位思考的矛盾处理</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">做法</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">加强团队的直面冲突的处理能力</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">对业绩提升有直接的帮助。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解法查看</span>“<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">冲突处理</span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">”</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">第三、</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">团队对话升级的能力</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">从</span>“</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">不欢而散</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">/</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">无效沟通</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">”</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的困境察觉，到团队有</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">共同设计对话方向</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的能力</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解法查看</span>“<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">对话升级</span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">”</span></span></p>','2021-12-31 05:41:03','2021-12-31 09:14:59'),(10,'凝聚力不足、合力不够，怎么办？','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-right: 0.0000pt; margin-left: 0.0000pt; mso-para-margin-right: 0.0000gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0.0000gd; text-indent: 0.0000pt; mso-char-indent-count: 0.0000; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; mso-pagination: none; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\" align=\"justify\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;\">一、</span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">凝聚</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">第一类痛点</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">1<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">目标缺乏热情，不关心公司长远发展。对目标坚持的程度不够，以及成员的投入度和努力度不够</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">2<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、留意：</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">团队中是否</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">过过于关</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">注短期的指标分解，有没有单独的时间去探讨未来的画面或企业的价值创造。通常管理者认为定好目标不需要和团队沟通，直接拆活派给他们就好。同时在执行过程进行量化的监管，这样的管理方式容易让团队只看到局部或非常短视，</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">导致不</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">关注整体。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解法：</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">可以发挥团队目标的意义感，</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">查看小程序中「</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">使命共振</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">联盟</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">个体价值</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">共创愿景</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">」</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-right: 0.0000pt; margin-left: 0.0000pt; mso-para-margin-right: 0.0000gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0.0000gd; text-indent: 0.0000pt; mso-char-indent-count: 0.0000; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; mso-pagination: none; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\" align=\"justify\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;\">二、</span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">凝聚</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">第二类痛点</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">1<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">目标放弃太快</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">背离目标的行为不指出。执行的承诺度也不够。</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">不清楚</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">对目标的认可度和理解度的真实想法。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">2<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">留意</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">：</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">是否</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">依赖</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">单向的指令去宣讲目标。团队有没有机会对宣讲的内容做出反馈和有没有倾听他们如何看待。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">单向的宣讲虽然看起来最高效，但容易出现团队觉得不该问或者问了之后怕领导认为自己有问题不敢问，下属不会反馈真实想法，容易形成理解的偏差和表面应付。管理者以为自己沟通很清楚，但过一段时间发现执行和交代不一致的时候，再去纠偏延误战机。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">3<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">针对这类痛点的解决，可以通过进行双向的沟通，多去主动地探寻同事的看法、观点和疑问，让这种双向的参与感去提高目标的认同感和承诺度。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"> </p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解法查看</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">小程序中</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">「</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\">目标共振</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">共见</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\">目标</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">重要性</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">」</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">三、凝聚</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">第三类痛点，</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">1<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">当团队关系上有不凝聚</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">容易产生冲突，互相的焦点和理解也都不一致。感觉前中后台容易有矛盾，发力点也不够聚焦。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-right: 0.0000pt; margin-left: 0.0000pt; mso-para-margin-right: 0.0000gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0.0000gd; text-indent: 0.0000pt; mso-char-indent-count: 0.0000; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; mso-pagination: none; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo2;\" align=\"justify\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;\">2、</span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解决方向一：</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">注意</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">如果一味的用自己认为正确的方向反复地重复指令</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">实现</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">思想统一</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">是比较低效的，</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">有可能</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">假的一致或表现</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">应付</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，缺乏真正的理解。面对矛盾和不聚焦的情况</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">是否有去倾听和探寻真正的差异点和矛盾点在哪里？</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">引导团队直面分歧的焦点沟通。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解法</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">查看小程序中</span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">「</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">分歧管理」</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"> </span><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;\">3、</span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解决方向二：</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">通过一起对齐目标和策略的产生过程</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，促进一致性；</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"> </p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解法查看小程序中「</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">目标共创</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">明确策略</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">」</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">4<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解决方案</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">三：</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">提高</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">成员的合作技能</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"> </p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">要留意。是否过度的看重传人成员的专业能力。强调业务和技术牛，但忽视了团队合作成员的合作基础。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"> </p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">可以持续落地的思路，建立团队认可的互动规范，在互动交流中鼓励彼此尊重和差异化观点的表达，例如有分歧不简单的评价，多探寻观点背后的推理，帮助团队进行建设性对话的合作能力。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">5<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解决</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">方向</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">四：</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"> </p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">营造一个安全的沟通氛围，帮助团队从较浅的表面沟通到深层次的沟通，这是有助于冲突和分歧的管理</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">管理者留意，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">成员有顾虑是带着盔甲表达</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">还是</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">很自然的交流，</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">或</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">容易</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">陷入</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">防守和进攻的状态。如果这种情形非常明显，</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">要主动管理，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">可以开诚布公的</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">探讨应对</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"> </p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解法查看小程序中「</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 21px; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">管理沟通阻碍</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 21px; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">」</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">四、凝聚</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">第四类痛点：</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"> </p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">1<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">对</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">目标缺乏热情，对公司和团队的归属管不够，大家融合度和认可感不够</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">2<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">要留意。团队成员有没有较为一致的价值取向</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">或者这种价值取向只是管理者单方面拎出来单向的在宣传</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">单项传递价值观不能实现增加归属感的作用。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-right: 0.0000pt; margin-left: 0.0000pt; mso-para-margin-right: 0.0000gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0.0000gd; text-indent: 0.0000pt; mso-char-indent-count: 0.0000; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; mso-pagination: none; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l2 level1 lfo3;\" align=\"justify\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;\">3、</span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">针对这类痛点的解法，可以帮助团队提取共享的价值观，提取的方向可以从面向未来的任务要求，也可以源于团队过去精神的提取，最重要的是要落实在大家共同熟悉的情境和行为体现上</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解法查看小程序中：「</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">共享价值观，氛围板块</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">」</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"> </p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><img src=\"http://xin-engine.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/tinymce/images/f311bcff5cbafe5fc7dee862ba6c821b61dbe8c76172a.jpeg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"> </p>','2021-12-31 06:20:26','2022-01-13 13:48:04'),(11,'团队效率如何提升？','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">一、</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">效率不高</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">三种情况：</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">释义</span>1<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">：人效</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，看两个方面</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">-</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">降本：识别「价值创造」的主要环节，次要环节「低成本」；</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">-</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">增效：管控</span>VS<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">激发自主性</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">释义</span>2<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">：</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">内部效率</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，检视三个方面</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">-</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">结构激励机制</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">-</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">团队运作</span>-<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">沟通</span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">&</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">协作效率</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">-</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">上下和左右传递和配合</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">释义</span>3<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">：「广义」团队的有效和高效</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">高绩效团队有</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">三个衡量指标：绩效</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">符合外部预期</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、团队</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">冲突掌控能力高且运作磨损少</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、个体</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">满意度和努力度高。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">二、</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">效率不够</span>—<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">关联要素</span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">1</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">任务层面的</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">「</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">适宜性</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">」</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，目标</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">方向</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">适应外部环境需要</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">「不匹配」或「外部关注不够」</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，导致</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">推进慢、前线怨言多等</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解法查看：「对齐」、「策略」版块</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">三、</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">效率不够</span>—<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">关联要素</span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">2</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">1<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">方向</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">理解的</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">「</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">一致</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">性」</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">不一致</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">会</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">导致变形、低效、损耗等</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">2<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">检查四个维度</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">：</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">-</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">高层方向</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">是否</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">清晰和共识</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">-</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">上下</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">传递</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">「</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">目标</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">路径打法</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">」</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">清晰和一致</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">-</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">左右</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">理解</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">「</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">关键打法</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">配合优先级</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">」一致</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">-<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">感知</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">明显</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">分歧</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">点是效率阻碍点，针对处理</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解法查看：「分歧处理」、「共识策略」、「上下对齐」、「左右对齐」等</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">四、</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">效率不够</span>—<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">关联要素</span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">3</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">1<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">策略路径打法</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的维度，看效率影响点。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">2<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">检查四个维度</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">-<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">是否</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">清晰</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">-<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">是否</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">聚焦：</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">对</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">VS</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">对</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">之间</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">聚焦的重点</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">-<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">是否有</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">策略路径</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">依赖</span>&</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">惯性局限性</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">-<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">是否有</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">策略</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">有误或不适应变化</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解法查看：「策略突破」、「槽点改进」、「复盘改进」、「策略共创」</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">五、</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">效率不够</span>—<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">关联要素</span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">4</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">1<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、从</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">合适的成员</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">角度，检视效率影响点；</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">2<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">检查维度</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">-</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">针对低</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">效</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的点，盘点能力</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的缺失或不足</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">-</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">团队合作能力</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">是否足够</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">引起协作损耗。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解法查看：「能力盘点」、「管理沟通阻碍」、「萃取经验」</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">六、</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">效率不够</span>—<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">关联要素</span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">5</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">1<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、从</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">有力执行</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的角度，检视推进效率；</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">2<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">检查维度</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">-</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">问题解决</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">能力</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">快速</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">推进</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">卡点</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">-</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">协作执行，</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">协作</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">行动的</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">有力</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">对焦</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">-</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">日常</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">执行，清晰</span>&<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">细化</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解法查看：「问题解决」、「协作行动对焦」、「行动规划」</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">七、效率不够</span>-<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">关联要素</span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">6</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">1<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">结构</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">大要素，有三点子要素</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">-</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">角色定位和分工</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，是否</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">适应外部的业务流畅度</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">匹配</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">关键</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">打法；</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">-</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">系统保障</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，在</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">人</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">财</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">物</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">信息</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">（沟通链路）</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">方面</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">是否</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">顺畅；</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">-</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">执行</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">协调</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">过程中，是否</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">兼顾</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">「利益相关者」，减少卡点；</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解法查看：「角色分工」、「策略落地」、「对齐相关者」等；</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">八、</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">效率不够</span>-<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">关联要素</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">7</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">团队运作，是指</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">人的协作、沟通、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">矛盾和冲突</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">处理</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，包括三个子维度</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-right: 0.0000pt; margin-left: 0.0000pt; mso-para-margin-right: 0.0000gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0.0000gd; text-indent: 0.0000pt; mso-char-indent-count: 0.0000; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; mso-pagination: none; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\" align=\"justify\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;\">1、</span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">有效</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">和深度的沟通，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">影响</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">最后的决策的</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">认同度</span>&<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">执行力</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-right: 0.0000pt; margin-left: 0.0000pt; mso-para-margin-right: 0.0000gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0.0000gd; text-indent: 0.0000pt; mso-char-indent-count: 0.0000; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; mso-pagination: none; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\" align=\"justify\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;\">2、</span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">冲突有效管理</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，没管理好</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">推开彼此，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">影响</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">效率</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-right: 0.0000pt; margin-left: 0.0000pt; mso-para-margin-right: 0.0000gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0.0000gd; text-indent: 0.0000pt; mso-char-indent-count: 0.0000; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; mso-pagination: none; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\" align=\"justify\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;\">3、</span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">团队的学习</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，是指针对提升</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">内部效率</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的学习</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">不断</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">超越过去</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解法查看：「分歧管理」、「冲突处理」、「学习板块」；</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">九</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、效率不够</span>-<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">关联要素</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">8</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">成员的「</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">动力</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">激发</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">」</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">——</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">投入度</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">和战斗力；</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">1<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、激发战斗力</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">要素一：目标的「意义感」</span>&<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">「认可度」 </span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">意义感</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，可以</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">激发个体持续动力和韧性</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">认可度</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，可以带动</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">参与感</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">热情</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">和投入度</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解法查看：「凝聚」板块，及各类「双向沟通」的研讨会；</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">2</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、激发战斗力要素</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">二</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">：成员</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的内驱力</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">挑</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">有内驱力的</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">人</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">是重点</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，同时了解</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">内驱力的</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">阻力</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">有哪些情况</span>:<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">比如</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">协调</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">一系列</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">不能直接管控的</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">人和事</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">任务安排过于</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">分散</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、不适合激发自主性的</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">文化氛围</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">等。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解法查看：「自主文化」、「明确行动焦点」</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">3</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、激发战斗力要素</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">三</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">：</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">安全感、信任</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">--<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">这些影响</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">成员三</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">个</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">状态</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，都与成员执行力和</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">动力</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">有关。</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">「</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">精神面貌</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">」：</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">有活力</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">主观能动性高</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">；</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">「</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">行为</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">语言」：</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">参与贡献</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">表达意见</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">；「情绪</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">感受</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">」：</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">正向的体验</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">高的能量。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">--<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">影响链路：</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">「</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">割裂</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">对立</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">」「单边宣讲」的模式</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，导致</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">成员「</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">戒备</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">防御</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">」</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，行为上显得「</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">不表达、表面认同、情绪卡顿</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">」，</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">影响执行力</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解法查看：「信任」板块</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">--<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">怎么做：</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">「人</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">被感召、尊重、认可</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">」</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">激发</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">价值贡献</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的动力</span>VS</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">人</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">「</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">需要强惩罚</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">管控</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">」才可以加强执行力。</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">业务特点和成员特点，需要怎样</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的氛围和理念</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，才能支撑</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">想要的行为</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">；</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解法查看：「氛围」板块</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">4</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、激发战斗力要素</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">四</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">：</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">应对</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">剧烈变化</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">「</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">外部</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">危机</span>&<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">挑战」</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">必不可少，在低谷和变换期能快速</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">恢复能量</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">提升</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">动力</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解法查看：「</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">士气</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">」</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">板块</span></span></p>','2021-12-31 13:52:03','2022-01-13 13:55:35'),(12,'对目标认同度和理解度不够？','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">这个问题，隐含假设是方向策略都很清晰，成员的</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">认同理解度不够。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">如果是这种情形，通常是团队中「有效沟通」做得不够。</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">有效沟通</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">是指</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">团队成员之间的交流、互动能够有效共享信息、做出决策、巩固关系</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">认同和理解度不够，对业务的影响是：成员对决策的投入度和承诺度不够，会体现出没有热情或缺乏动力。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-right: 0.0000pt; mso-para-margin-right: 0.0000gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0.0000gd; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; mso-pagination: none; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\" align=\"justify\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;\">1、</span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">可能的相关原因：</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-right: 0.0000pt; margin-left: 21.0000pt; mso-para-margin-right: 0.0000gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0.0000gd; text-indent: -21.0000pt; mso-char-indent-count: 0.0000; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; mso-pagination: none; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo2;\" align=\"justify\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Wingdings; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;\">&Oslash;&nbsp;</span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">单项宣讲型沟通</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; text-indent: -28px;\">单项宣讲型沟通，容易让</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">成员有戒备和无价值感，</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">行为体现出「不想说、不敢说」等，对结果容易</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">表面认同或认同度不够</span><span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">，这些都会导致</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">执行动力不足或有偏差。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-right: 0.0000pt; margin-left: 21.0000pt; mso-para-margin-right: 0.0000gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0.0000gd; text-indent: -21.0000pt; mso-char-indent-count: 0.0000; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; mso-pagination: none; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l2 level1 lfo3;\" align=\"justify\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Wingdings; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;\">&Oslash;&nbsp;</span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">宣讲之后问了反馈，团队没想法</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">这种情形，需要检视员工有没有安全感的氛围，有合适的环境让成员「敢说、愿意说、和轻松说」。如果</span>Leader<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">姿态上体现的是&ldquo;我定出来宣讲就够了，效率第一&rdquo;等，或者团队有意见领袖容易无意识的攻击</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">成员</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">想法等，这种氛围都会让员工感受到：&ldquo;不是真的需要大家的声音&rdquo;，容易产生防御和担心，觉得「不该问、或问了之后怕领导认为自己有问题不敢问」，下属不会反馈真实想法，容易形成理解的偏差和表面应付。管理者以为自己沟通很清楚，但过一段时间发现执行和交代不一致的时候，再去纠偏延误战机。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-right: 0.0000pt; margin-left: 21.0000pt; mso-para-margin-right: 0.0000gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0.0000gd; text-indent: -21.0000pt; mso-char-indent-count: 0.0000; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; mso-pagination: none; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l3 level1 lfo4;\" align=\"justify\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Wingdings; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;\">&Oslash;&nbsp;</span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">谈话深度不够</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">通常表达市场判断的时候，多数直接给的是最后的判断和分析。如果在观点层面无法达成一致，需要深入到基本假设去探寻彼此的差异，促进深度交流和明晰分歧点。个体在形成观点时有三个层次的不同，从三个层次帮助成员探寻观点和促进深度对话，第一个层次是个人看到的事实不同；第二个层次是挑选的信息和赋予的含义不同；第三个是对赋予的含义和给出的回应和行动也不同。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">2<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、解法方向：</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">创造双向沟通的机会。一种是即使想得很清楚，把分析的过程提出来一起共创；另一种方式是宣讲并分享推理过程，同时用集体反馈的技巧，让成员参与表达。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Wingdings; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;\">&Oslash;&nbsp;</span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">为什么</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">双向沟通，可以增加理解和</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">认可度？</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">这个背后的逻辑是参与的机会让</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">成员</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">表达过</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">他</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的一些顾虑</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">看法、诉求，对于最终</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">他</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">认为</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">决策</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，已经</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">包含</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">自己</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的一部分，这个感觉会增强，所以</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">对认同度</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">会有帮助的。微妙的地方</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">是，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">如果</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">成员</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">觉得这一切都是</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">操纵</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，那就反作用</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: Wingdings;\">&Oslash;</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解法查看：「目标共振、目标共创、策略共创、讨论目标重要性」，解法可以灵活变通，最重要的是根据情景的需要，创建双向沟通的过程，并有机会对背后的推论有深度对话的机会。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">最重要的是管理者要有耐心放下「自己讲效率第一、团队想法不够」等这样的心态。比起表面认同延误战机，这样的双向沟通会，反而效率更高，同时深度的探讨帮助成员间高质量的理解。</span></span></p>','2021-12-31 23:24:25','2022-01-04 07:59:03'),(13,'执行变形，怎么办','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">1<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、原因可能性</span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">1</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">：成员</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">心里不认同，</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">或</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">理解错了</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">这种情况</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">和成员间</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">有效沟通有关</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，第一、有没有双向沟通和深度的对话，这是认同和理解的基础；第二、有没有营造安全感的宣讲氛围，好的氛围让成员表达真实反馈，相反，形成防御、戒备，导致</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">不敢说</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、不愿意说，怕说错。听不到真实想法的原因有：团队有成员很强势会攻击评价别人、</span><span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">表达意见时感受到被指责影响会议效率等，这些情形容易导致假共识、或理解偏差，而执行的结果又有滞后性。</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">「关于不认同和不理解」详细请看<span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">：</span></span></span><span style=\"font-family: Nunito; line-height: 28px; color: #414750; letter-spacing: 0.15pt; font-size: 10pt; background-color: #f8fafc;\"><a href=\"https://www.xteamengine.com/knowledge/12\">https://www.xteamengine.com/knowledge/12</a></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">2<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、原因可能性</span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">2</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">：</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">结构性的原因</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">可能激励考核的方式跟</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">业务</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">方向不匹配，或甚至与之冲突。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 解法可参考小程序：「策略落地六要素」；</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">3<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、原因可能性</span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">3</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">：方向说得</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">不够聚焦，</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">太</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">宽泛，执行时发力分散，焦点没对齐。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;解法可参考小程序：「明确策略」「行动对焦」等。</span></p>','2021-12-31 23:37:40','2022-01-08 04:11:51'),(14,'策略落不下去，怎么办？','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">1<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、可能原因之一：</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">大的公司级的策略</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、关键战役和路径</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">有可能不清</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">或过于宽泛</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解法查看「目标共振、明确策略」</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">2<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、可能原因之二：部门级领了任务，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">没有什么方法做策略分解。</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">比如</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">公司级</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">策略</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">明确，部门级的关键行动不见得是明确的，落不下去其实是跟模糊有关系的</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解法查看「策略共创、左右对齐」</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">3<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、可能原因之三：往下推的时候，左右的协调沟通容易形成卡点。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">有效沟通就会比较侧重在跨边界的沟通</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">跨层级</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的沟通。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">**<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">一种卡点是遇到冲突和分歧，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">不同层级</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">和</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">不同部门最容易出现视角差异比较大，导致发生冲突。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解决方式：训练掌控冲突的能力至关重要。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">**<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">另一种卡点是管理层</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">刻意回避冲突，遇到了阻力，不想去面对</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">卡点</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解决方式：强化文化-</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">直面卡点</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">和</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">直面</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">分歧</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">留意：协调沟通的问题，机制解决不是首选，有可能导团队致</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">进一步的回避沟通，</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">大家很习惯一谈到</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">沟通</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">就想到协同的</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">沟通机制，容易把其僵化处理</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解法查看：「个人复盘学习、中层流程穿越、分歧处理」等</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">4<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">可能原因之</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">四</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">：</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">落地时</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">系统性保障不够</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解法查看：「策略落地」</span></span></p>','2021-12-31 23:58:03','2022-01-08 04:13:40'),(15,'横向部门，沟通浮于表面和回避协同沟通，容易形成推诿。','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;\">1、</span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">一方面</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">肯定</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">和成员间的</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">信任</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">和沟通有关。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">通常直接提升个体沟通能力对该类问题帮助不大，但信任的解法会有一定程度的帮助，可以让成员间的关系和戒备有些松动，更容易形成改变。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">2<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、另一方面，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">横向之间这种的不沟通或者回避冲突矛盾</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的沟通方式</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，很有可能是</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">团队</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">有一个不良的沟通模式存在，</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">这个部分又和</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">信任是一个扭结的关系。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">最高效的办法从发现「</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">沟通模式</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">」</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">着手，</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">观察平时工作时成员的</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">实际对话过程，</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">发现</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">有可能长期导致了他们回避冲突</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的模式。这个领域属于「团体动力学」，需要专门的教练。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">「把反复出现问题的源头</span>&mdash;<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">团队互动的模式」显性化，是解决互动动力问题的窄门和捷径。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>','2022-01-01 00:10:07','2022-01-01 00:10:07'),(16,'业务模糊','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: 21.0000pt; mso-para-margin-left: 0.0000gd; text-indent: -21.0000pt; mso-char-indent-count: 0.0000; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">第一种情形，焦点在方向模糊。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: 21.0000pt; mso-para-margin-left: 0.0000gd; text-indent: -21.0000pt; mso-char-indent-count: 0.0000; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\">1<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、可能原因</span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">1</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">：重要的相关者有分歧、或者诉求不明确没有表达、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">不一致</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，特别是高管团队的分歧，会让成员感受到业务的模糊性。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: 21.0000pt; mso-para-margin-left: 0.0000gd; text-indent: -21.0000pt; mso-char-indent-count: 0.0000; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\">2<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、可能原因</span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">2</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">：适应外部的变化，不够敏锐。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: 21.0000pt; mso-para-margin-left: 0.0000gd; text-indent: -21.0000pt; mso-char-indent-count: 0.0000; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;外部已经发生变化，有些人感知到并做出应对，有些人没有跟上，步调不一致。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: 21.0000pt; mso-para-margin-left: 0.0000gd; text-indent: -21.0000pt; mso-char-indent-count: 0.0000; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;这种情形焦点在策略和打法模糊。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: 21.0000pt; mso-para-margin-left: 0.0000gd; text-indent: -21.0000pt; mso-char-indent-count: 0.0000; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; text-align: justify;\">3</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; text-align: justify; font-family: 宋体;\">、</span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">策略过于宽泛，公司级的策略有没有清晰，通常把指标拆解拍下去，成员对策略路径没有共识，容易出现策略过于宽泛和焦点不明确，大家对资源投放的重点，以及共同的优先级没有共识。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: 21.0000pt; mso-para-margin-left: 0.0000gd; text-indent: -21.0000pt; mso-char-indent-count: 0.0000; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; text-align: justify;\">4</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; text-align: justify; font-family: 宋体;\">、</span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">执行不明确不具体，在执行推进过程中，各类行动规划是否做到及时梳理和调整，特别是协作部门间的行动对焦，毕竟跨部门的日常执行沟通较少。</span></span></p>','2022-01-01 00:22:45','2022-01-04 08:06:32'),(17,'推进慢','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">1<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、可能原因</span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">1</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">：</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">适宜性</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">相关</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">方向策略是否符合外部变化，需要检视前线和客户等信号的理解有没有误差。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解法查看「对齐」版块；</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">2<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、可能原因</span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">2</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">：目标多，且较分散</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">关键任务的焦点是否明确，特别是跨职能的关键任务，大家理解的资源投放重点是否一致。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解法查看「行动对焦、明确策略」等，让优先级的理解明确、聚焦、且无分歧。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-right: 0.0000pt; margin-left: 0.0000pt; mso-para-margin-right: 0.0000gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0.0000gd; text-indent: 0.0000pt; mso-char-indent-count: 0.0000; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; mso-pagination: none; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\" align=\"justify\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;\">3、</span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">可能原因</span>3<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">：</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">策略是否有效</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">策略有误，通常会体现出「推进慢或结果产出不够符合客户预期」。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解法查看「洞察客户、策略共创」</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-right: 0.0000pt; margin-left: 0.0000pt; mso-para-margin-right: 0.0000gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0.0000gd; text-indent: 0.0000pt; mso-char-indent-count: 0.0000; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; mso-pagination: none; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\" align=\"justify\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;\">4、</span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">可能原因</span>4<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">：</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">横向</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">沟通的卡点</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">包括在执行时横向协作沟通中</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">回避矛盾</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，会影响推进。或横向协作陷入</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">固有流程</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，流程机制不能灵活匹配业务需要。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-right: 0.0000pt; margin-left: 0.0000pt; mso-para-margin-right: 0.0000gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0.0000gd; text-indent: 0.0000pt; mso-char-indent-count: 0.0000; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; mso-pagination: none; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\" align=\"justify\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;\">5、</span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">可能原因</span>5<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">：</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">上下</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">推进有影响</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">比如执行中，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">决策权</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">下放不够，决策效率跟不上业务需要。</span></span></p>','2022-01-01 00:50:30','2022-01-04 08:09:30'),(18,'协作不高效','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: 21.0000pt; mso-para-margin-left: 0.0000gd; text-indent: -21.0000pt; mso-char-indent-count: 0.0000; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Wingdings; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;\">l&nbsp;</span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">协作不高效</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;\">第一、</span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">激励机制</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">有些机制太强调个体，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">对于跨职能的关键任务没有专项设定</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，常有的方法有设定专项小组的考核、互设</span>KPI<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">等；</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解法方向：设定协同小组的机制、部门间互设KPI等；</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解法参考小程序中：「共识关键策略、明确关键任务」，在这个基础上，根据任务需要设置相应机制。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: 0.0000pt; mso-para-margin-left: 0.0000gd; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo2;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;\">第二、</span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">与</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">角色</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">分工有关系</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，职责边界</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">模糊，分歧点较多；</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解法参考小程序中：「角色分工」、「中层流程穿越活动」</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">第三、与团队运作有关，有三点子维度。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">--</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">有效对话：团队成员之间的交流、互动能够有效共享信息、做出决策、巩固关系</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">--</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">掌控冲突：在目标、行动不兼容的情况下，能够有效处理分歧，建设性地利用冲突</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">--</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">快速学习：团队在完成任务的过程中，通过反思，作为一个整体，越来越有效</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解法参考小程序中：「管理沟通阻碍」、「分歧冲突处理」、「心智模式翻转」等</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;\">第四、</span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">部门负责人格局和心智有关</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">比如对整体的关注度不够，容易产生沟通误解等情况，Leader能有自我内在调整的能力，以及&ldquo;链接式&rdquo;的</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">沟通技能，会促进协作。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解法参考小程序中：</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">「心智模式翻转」、</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">「个人反思」、「沟通升级」等；</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;\">第五、</span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">和信任有关，成员间缺乏比较深的关系品质，这种关系品质和信任可以支持跨部门间沟通的意愿度，成员间敢沟通、愿意表达是基础。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解法参考小程序中：「角色认可」、「对话升级」、「共同理解」、「挖掘团队资源」等；</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\" align=\"justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">其他原因分析，参考「任务推进慢」：</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><a href=\"https://www.xteamengine.com/knowledge/17\">https://www.xteamengine.com/knowledge/17</a></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\" align=\"justify\">&nbsp;</p>','2022-01-02 23:13:45','2022-01-07 13:25:41'),(19,'不关心整体&没归属感','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-right: 0.0000pt; margin-left: 0.0000pt; mso-para-margin-right: 0.0000gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0.0000gd; text-indent: 0.0000pt; mso-char-indent-count: 0.0000; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; mso-pagination: none; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\" align=\"justify\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;\">第一、</span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">团队缺乏</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">意义</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">感和</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">认同</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">感，这两点是高效团队的「关键要素」，「意义感」可以帮助团队关心整体、对共同目标更有热情和凝聚；</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解法查看：「共振使命</span>/<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">愿景」、「</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">联盟个体」、「共识价值」等凝聚版块</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-right: 0.0000pt; margin-left: 0.0000pt; mso-para-margin-right: 0.0000gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0.0000gd; text-indent: 0.0000pt; mso-char-indent-count: 0.0000; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; mso-pagination: none; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\" align=\"justify\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;\">第二、</span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">断层和割裂，造成员工不关心整体</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">日常容易关注</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">被分割的</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">短期</span>KPI<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，造成</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">团队</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">短视和割裂，</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">所以留意拆细节和盯细节的管理模式，建议的方式提高目标的认可度和清晰的颗粒度，在执行方面用灵活的结构和机制让团队在共同目标下运作。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">这也是团队建设的重要方向：彼此互赖可以更好的完成共同任务。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解法留意：机制层面太强调「关注个体的局部任务」，自然会削弱「关注整体性」的另一面。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">第三、管理者的合作能力</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">员工能关注整体，和中层管理者</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">合作技能</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">有关，比如关心整体有</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">格局、愿意</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">传递连接信息等，在高效团队的关键要素中，成员需</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">兼具</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">业务能力</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">与合作技能</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。往往强调关注业务能力，对合作的能力强化不够。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">如果中层传递给员工的</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">宏观画面比较清楚，会</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">让团队</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">对大目标比较关切，如果中层</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">只站在自己的立场，传递下去容易造成断层，和不关注整体。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解法参考：「中层流程穿越」</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-right: 0.0000pt; margin-left: 0.0000pt; mso-para-margin-right: 0.0000gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0.0000gd; text-indent: 0.0000pt; mso-char-indent-count: 0.0000; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; mso-pagination: none; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo2;\" align=\"justify\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;\">第四、</span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">信任</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">和</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">关系品质</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">团队间的信任和关系品质，会影响成员活力、行为等，信任不足，会表现出「戒备、不愿意沟通、有情绪抵抗」等情况，自然影响到归属感和对整体的关切度。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解法参考：「信任」版块</span></span></p>','2022-01-03 03:03:38','2022-01-04 08:15:02'),(20,'缺乏热情、轻言放弃','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-right: 0.0000pt; mso-para-margin-right: 0.0000gd; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; mso-pagination: none; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo2;\" align=\"justify\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;\">1、</span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">提高对目标的认同感</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 22px; font-size: 11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，有决心克服困难的状态</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; line-height: 22px; font-size: 11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">；</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"line-height: 22px; font-size: 11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">实现成员对目标和打法认同，做法是通过创造双向沟通的机会，会影响成员的投入度和执行力。方式是通过提升参与感，让成员觉得最后的决策与自己的参与有关的感受更强烈，更能调动热情和认可度。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"line-height: 22px; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"line-height: 22px; font-size: 11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解法参考：「目标共创、策略共创、探讨目标重要性」等</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-right: 0.0000pt; mso-para-margin-right: 0.0000gd; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; mso-pagination: none; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo2;\" align=\"justify\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;\">2、</span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">与员工的内驱力有关，挑选有心理韧性的成员，会自带热情，特别是创业团队。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">当然也留意高内驱力的人，会有一些情形容易降低热情和积极性。比如任务过于复杂，要推动一系列不能直接掌控的人事物；比如任务过于发散、容易变化，成员总在调整关注点；比如氛围与年轻员工需要的自主性环境相反等。都会影响到成员的热情和投入度。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">3<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、文化和氛围的影响</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">比如团队过往历史中，一直体现出对一个创新想法很有热情，但是团队转变方向很快，潜意识中会让团队认为</span>&ldquo;<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">反正有热情也没用，过一段时间管理层就变了</span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">这些是隐性的影响，通常出现在历史久一些的团队，所以要了解真实的声音，以及留意成员间认为</span>&ldquo;<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">理所当然</span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的潜意识假设。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>','2022-01-03 03:07:27','2022-01-04 08:16:32'),(21,'隔阂不直言','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-right: 0.0000pt; margin-left: 21.0000pt; mso-para-margin-right: 0.0000gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0.0000gd; text-indent: -21.0000pt; mso-char-indent-count: 0.0000; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; mso-pagination: none; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\" align=\"justify\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;\">1、</span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">心里安全感是主要因素</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">戒备是成员在安全感不足的</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">环境中</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，长期长出来的。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">成员表达意见有人评判和被攻击、当表达不同意见时就会引起很差的情绪体验等，这些都会强化</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">安全感不足的氛围，进一步让成员</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\">不敢说、不愿意说、怕评判、怕犯错，以及对成员有刻板印象。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解法：如何创造这样的氛围，改善成员的状态，帮助团队做到真诚和透明的沟通。这是一条窄门，可以解决根本，但是往往效果没有立竿见影，需要营造持续性支持的文化，让大家彼此尊重，感觉很安全，愿意表达观点。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-right: 0.0000pt; margin-left: 0.0000pt; mso-para-margin-right: 0.0000gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0.0000gd; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; mso-pagination: none; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo2;\" align=\"justify\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;\">2、</span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">沟通模式</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-right: 0.0000pt; mso-para-margin-right: 0.0000gd; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; mso-pagination: none; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l2 level1 lfo3;\" align=\"justify\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;\">第一、</span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">训练真诚沟通的内在状态，指向管理者</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;\">向内觉察的沟通训练</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\">。</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\">沟通模式转变，直接影响了合作效率和关系质量，长期就影响了信任的氛围。</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解决方向：个体沟通的心智模式升级，可以参考「沟通升级、对话升级」；</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">第二、隔阂很有可能是目前的团队困在僵化的沟通方式中，而这种方式低效和无效，大家的情感体验都不好，这个僵化的方式是指重复的会出现某种情况，这种重复的情况会让任务卡顿，回避冲突或者压制表达。大部分都能感知到，但对背后的模式和因果关系很难看清楚，容易困在里面，这样的状态需要外部的视角去打破。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解决方向：看见人际互动中的彼此互动的模式。找外部行动教练，直接观察到团队之间的「互动模式</span>&mdash;&mdash;<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">反复出现问题的源头」。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">具体做法就是团队在日常业务沟通场景中，观察这种模式，</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">把盲点和隐形的互动源头「显性化」互相看见，共见这个盲点，共识共同改变的行动计划和行为约束规则，是高效和最有效的办法</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;\">3、</span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">信任</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">信任可持续的基础是「成员间真诚透明的沟通行为」，信任可持续的收益是「心理安全的氛围」，这些直接影响的是成员沟通意愿、真实表达的可能性、关系的品质等。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解决方向，从信任开始去破，从团建入手，松动和软化关系的状态。</span></span></p>','2022-01-03 03:11:23','2022-01-04 08:19:58'),(22,'部门墙、推诿','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-right: 0.0000pt; mso-para-margin-right: 0.0000gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0.0000gd; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; mso-pagination: none; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo2;\" align=\"justify\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;\">1、</span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">有可能是高层</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">冲突，导致中层的</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">割裂</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">；</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解法参考：「冲突处理」或帮助直面冲突的「信任」版块；</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-right: 0.0000pt; margin-left: 0.0000pt; mso-para-margin-right: 0.0000gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0.0000gd; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; mso-pagination: none; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo2;\" align=\"justify\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;\">2、</span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">左右</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">部门</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">焦点</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">矛盾</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">当左右对关键任务、任务优先级等理解不一致，或各有看法时，容易造成部门墙。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解法参考：「共识策略、左右对齐、对焦协同行动」等。但最重要的是感受卡在什么矛盾焦点，让团队直面这个矛盾焦点，参考「分歧处理」。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-right: 0.0000pt; margin-left: 0.0000pt; mso-para-margin-right: 0.0000gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0.0000gd; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; mso-pagination: none; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo2;\" align=\"justify\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;\">3、</span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">结构上的分工和配合</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">让团队能够站在整体视角下，保持分工的开放性和对分工边界的灵活性，根据业务需要和关键战役的需要来调整。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">一层不变的结构，容易造成部门墙和不适应任务配合。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">另外，大部分公司用「不同职能划分部门」的结构，本来就有部门边界过强的特点。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解法参考：「清晰分工」。关键是管理者让团队站在整体最优的视角，并灵活匹配专项小组、拉通机制等。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">4<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、成员的合作技能</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"> </p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">通常是强调个人技能，忽视成员的</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">合作技能</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，容易造成团队分歧太多，或成员彼此有成见和偏见。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解法参考：「管理沟通阻碍」、「挖掘团队资源优势」等。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">5<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、管理层</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">格局</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，格局不够容易引发成员间的对立。比如无意识想证明对错、维护自尊等，对自己无意识的执念和情绪变化没有觉察，就容易因为观点不同引起对立，甚至破坏关系和引起隔阂和成见。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"> </p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解法参考：「</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">个人复盘</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、对话升级」等；</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">关于关系隔阂较深，查看</span></span><span style=\"caret-color: #414750; color: #414750; font-family: Nunito, Montserrat, system-ui, BlinkMacSystemFont, -apple-system, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.1599999964237213px; background-color: #f8fafc;\">https://www.xteamengine.com/knowledge/21</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">关于出问题互相推诿，查看</span></span><span style=\"caret-color: #414750; color: #414750; font-family: Nunito, Montserrat, system-ui, BlinkMacSystemFont, -apple-system, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.1599999964237213px; background-color: #f8fafc;\">https://www.xteamengine.com/knowledge/6</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"> </span></p>','2022-01-03 03:17:21','2022-01-04 13:14:36'),(23,'沟通氛围不佳','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">1<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、检查因素之一：有效沟通</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">是指成员能不能共享信息、能不能进行建设性对话，对话是停留在较浅还是较深的状态。</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">如果团队沟通都停留在较浅的层面，一方面不能深度共识，另一方面对话氛围演化成回避沟通和隔阂的状态。这种情形，成员会体验到沟通氛围不太对。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解决参考</span>:&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">「沟通升级」、「对话升级」、「对齐」版块等。或所有的「团队研讨」提升了成员的参与度，会促进双向沟通，和差异性观点的交互等。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">2<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">检查因素之一：</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\">信任维度</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">信任不足，直接影响成员「是否愿意表达、敢不敢表达」等沟通行为，大部分人际互动方面的困扰，都可以从信任的团建先入手去松动和软化僵化的关系。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解决参考「信任」版块。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-right: 0.0000pt; mso-para-margin-right: 0.0000gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0.0000gd; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; mso-pagination: none; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo2;\" align=\"justify\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;\">3、</span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">掌控冲突</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">沟通氛围差，往往伴随着争斗和冲突较多。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">如果形成不太</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">久的团队</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，及时用团队规范保持高效的行为，同时学习分歧和冲突处理来改善，</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">可以很好的帮助</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">长期滋养出好的氛围</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解法参考：「行为规范、分歧和冲突处理」。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">4<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、氛围和模式的影响</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">如果团队已经有一段时间历史，成员的沟通表现有可能被长期形成的某些规则所影响，长期的互动模式导致了心里防御的状态，需要回到起因「模式」上处理。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">团队被</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">困在僵化的</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">互动</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">方式中，而这种方式低效和无效，大家的情感体验都不好，这个僵化的方式是指重复的会出现某种情况，这种重复的情况会让任务卡顿，回避冲突或者压制表达。大部分都能感知到，但对背后的模式和因果关系很难看清楚，容易困在里面，这样的状态需要外部的视角去打破。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解决方向：</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">看见人际互动中的彼此互动的模式。找外部行动教练，直接观察到团队之间的「互动模式</span>&mdash;&mdash;<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">反复出现问题的源头」。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">具体做法就是团队在日常业务沟通场景中，去观察这种模式，把盲点和隐形的互动源头显性化互相看见，共见这个盲点，共识共同改变的行动计划和行为约束规则，是高效和最有效的办法。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>','2022-01-03 03:25:28','2022-01-04 13:16:43'),(24,'谈关系感受，对团队有什么作用？','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">团队的烦恼都包含了人际关系相处中，人与人相处的问题都在关系当中，所以需要回到关系当中才能解决，意味着如果我们要一起合作来完成一些事情，就无法规避所谓的关系。没有关系，无法合作并没有办法去创造合力，就变成单打独斗，不能团队作战。所以反过来，要团队作战，要让团队多元化发挥出来。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">因为这个原理，回到工作中，关系需要改进，而谈论感受是促进彼此情感链接，以及人际关系最主要的介入方式和最有效的改良方式。所以定期的情场，谈论感受的必要性是帮助合作关系加强。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">但阻力是在于，</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">管理者往往比较理性，沟通任务时，很少包含情感</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，或有信念认为成年人不需要谈及感受，很幼稚。这些信念都会影响关系品质的建立。</span></span></p>','2022-01-03 03:28:48','2022-01-03 03:28:48'),(25,'如何让员工统一管理语言？','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-right: 0.0000pt; margin-left: 21.0000pt; mso-para-margin-right: 0.0000gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0.0000gd; text-indent: -21.0000pt; mso-char-indent-count: 0.0000; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; mso-pagination: none; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\" align=\"justify\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">这个问题的前提</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">不是没有管理语言，</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">而是大家接受和践行的</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">非常不一样</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">统一管理语言</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">和文化交集非常高</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，具体要看</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">关于哪个方面的管理语言</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">着重想统一</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">如</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">绩效、策略、人员管理，运营过程</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">等，也要结合</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">业务过程</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的需要。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">中小公司可以找到适合的标杆管理做参考，</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">但是引入大厂的标杆管理方式，要检视是否匹配业务过程相关的绩效、策略、人员管理等特点。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">如果</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">已经有倾向性</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">样板</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">做标杆，</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">并监视了业务的符合程度，重点处理的是</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">植入的过程</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，这个过程也需要共同参与适用性的微创新，</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">形成内部共识语言系统</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。过程的重点，是</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">需要好的对话过程，逐步形成共识，术语定义和内涵的理解，</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">需要在双向对话的过程中形成团队自己的情景和行为理解，内化于心。同时也可以外显于形，</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">形成书面手册，培训教育方式不断传播。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">植入标杆文化的过程中，注意</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">微创新也</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">需要由</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">双向沟通和共识</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">会</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">而不是单项传递。同时也注意，不是一次性的安装植入文化，是和团队</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">持续</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">沟通、践行、迭代和进化而成的</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">中早期</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">团队</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">注意</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">不要</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">依赖大厂文化过度</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">管理，</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">毕竟阶段不同</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，不能僵化</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">处理</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">重要的是</span>CEO<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">有这个需求的时候，问问自己着重想改变的是什么现象？比如如果统一了管理语言，最期望看到的不一样是什么？焦点是在你着重处理的「转变」方面。如果是为了做而做，执行的人也有可能发力没有焦点和不明白背后的重要性。</span></span></p>','2022-01-03 03:47:22','2022-01-03 03:47:22'),(26,'公司目标如何与个人目标强联盟？','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"line-height: 18px; font-size: 9pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">首先，从</span></span><span style=\"line-height: 18px; font-size: 9pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">目标意义感出发，寻求共振</span></span><span style=\"line-height: 18px; font-size: 9pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">度，参考凝聚版块；作用力占比约</span>30%</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"line-height: 18px; font-size: 9pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">其次，从</span></span><span style=\"line-height: 18px; font-size: 9pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">结构激励系统，激发工作动能</span></span><span style=\"line-height: 18px; font-size: 9pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">；这个要素作用力占</span>50%<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">以上；</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"line-height: 18px; font-size: 9pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">最后，从团队</span></span><span style=\"line-height: 18px; font-size: 9pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">运作</span></span><span style=\"line-height: 18px; font-size: 9pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的好坏</span></span><span style=\"line-height: 18px; font-size: 9pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，</span></span><span style=\"line-height: 18px; font-size: 9pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">比如</span></span><span style=\"line-height: 18px; font-size: 9pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">有效沟通</span></span><span style=\"line-height: 18px; font-size: 9pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、好的</span></span><span style=\"line-height: 18px; font-size: 9pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">信任</span></span><span style=\"line-height: 18px; font-size: 9pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"line-height: 18px; font-size: 9pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">强情感纽带</span></span><span style=\"line-height: 18px; font-size: 9pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">关系等，愿不愿意在这里长期合作下去。这个作用约</span>20%<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"line-height: 18px; font-size: 9pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">但注意留意的是，激励除了物质，「感受和个体激」可以弥补物质不足，比如</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">关于心灵感受，个体成就感，做主的感觉，受尊重公平感觉</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">等，特别是激励不明确的中早期创业团队</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。</span></span></p>','2022-01-03 04:01:47','2022-01-03 04:01:47'),(27,'CEO想解决问题是，如何让团队能够认识到这件事的重要性？','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">这个需求背后往往期待有外部的人能搞定大家的共识。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">但看法的源头，</span>CEO<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">有2个潜意识假设：</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-right: 0.0000pt; mso-para-margin-right: 0.0000gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0.0000gd; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; mso-pagination: none; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\" align=\"justify\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;\">1、</span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">我要看的问题，不需要其他视角，一定是对的；</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-right: 0.0000pt; mso-para-margin-right: 0.0000gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0.0000gd; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; mso-pagination: none; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\" align=\"justify\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;\">2、</span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">我是这样想的，下面的人也需要是这样想的；</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">CEO<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">看到了团队的一个问题，一般潜意识的下一步是让团队和自己有一样的重视度。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">建议的做法：</span>CEO<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">看到了问题可以为大家做贡献，自己的想法和看到的影响都抛出来，看看团队怎么看待，有什么不同视角，也许最后结论是一样的，但是共识的品质和拥护度是完全不同的。及时看法不一样，也看到不同视角都如何理解，有没有一些盲点存在，或再看关键差异点在哪里和如何处理。</span></span></p>','2022-01-03 08:16:32','2022-01-03 08:16:50'),(28,'市场反应迟钝、外部感知意识不够','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">1<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、检查策略适宜性，是否符合外部的诉求</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">当不适应外部情况时，前线业务人员会感知比较明显，可以通过</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">前线复盘</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">来听到更多市场的变化反馈和洞察关键信息。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">同时和团队讨论打法和计划的时候，多用外部视角的维度来评估打法好坏。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解法参考：「洞察外部利益相关者、洞察客户、前线槽点改进」等。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;\">2、</span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">团队的能力是否匹配业务的变化</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">有可能外部已经变化，Leader主攻的方向和打法也有所调整，但是团队的能力没有及时梳理，也会出现市场反应迟钝，可以参考「盘点能力」，从外部变化的关键点，检视业务打法的适配性，回看团队能力的缺失和补齐等。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-right: 0.0000pt; margin-left: 0.0000pt; mso-para-margin-right: 0.0000gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0.0000gd; text-indent: 0.0000pt; mso-char-indent-count: 0.0000; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; mso-pagination: none; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\" align=\"justify\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;\">3、</span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">与团队有效沟通有关</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">比如团队成员知道有些做法不符合市场需要，但是存在不表达真实声音，不敢说、说了不听、不想说等各种几种情景。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解决思路：</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">从短期来讲，根据业务需求，可以组织单场的团队研讨会，用引导的方式带动参与感，并营造安全感的氛围，促进团队积极的表达真实声音和深度的沟通。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">从长期来讲，要看见造成这些现象的源头在哪里，比如</span>CEO<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">或团队</span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">Leader</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">风格过于强势（</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">360</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">成员</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">反馈</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">都指向这里有确定性</span>)</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">这些是让团队表达有防御的源头，那</span>leader<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">本人如果对自己的行为和对团队的影响能有觉察，是对团队最大的改善。</span></span></p>','2022-01-03 08:42:35','2022-01-04 13:18:01'),(29,'策略打法总是常规性做法，没有突破','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">一、如果是通过团队研讨的方式解决，需要突破局限性，关键点在于：</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-right: 0.0000pt; margin-left: 0.0000pt; mso-para-margin-right: 0.0000gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0.0000gd; text-indent: 0.0000pt; mso-char-indent-count: 0.0000; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; mso-pagination: none; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\" align=\"justify\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;\">1、</span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">对话质量，成员</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">参与感是否不足、愿不愿表达、能不能激发自由表达、有分歧时是转化成建设性的意见，还是造成情绪对立和不表达。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-right: 0.0000pt; margin-left: 0.0000pt; mso-para-margin-right: 0.0000gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0.0000gd; text-indent: 0.0000pt; mso-char-indent-count: 0.0000; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; mso-pagination: none; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\" align=\"justify\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;\">2、</span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">思维惯性的突破，可以通过邀请</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">成员多元化</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">视角，重点是识别和可以跳出思维方式相似点和局限性。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-right: 0.0000pt; margin-left: 0.0000pt; mso-para-margin-right: 0.0000gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0.0000gd; text-indent: 0.0000pt; mso-char-indent-count: 0.0000; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; mso-pagination: none; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\" align=\"justify\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;\">3、</span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">重视外部的视角，从客户视角的洞察，去激发思路创新。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">4<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、激发</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">创新性</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的推理过程</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">新信息</span>--<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">新理解</span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">--</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">新洞察</span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">--</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">新思路和行动，信息流动交互是突破的前提。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-right: 0.0000pt; margin-left: 0.0000pt; mso-para-margin-right: 0.0000gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0.0000gd; text-indent: 0.0000pt; mso-char-indent-count: 0.0000; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; mso-pagination: none; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo2;\" align=\"justify\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;\">二、</span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">隐形的氛围容易引发成员防御，阻碍思路突破</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">平时有可能不能突破，是有隐形的阻碍点，不能激发团队的深度沟通和创新，比如如果说出新的想法，会引发没必要的冲突，有可能是一直是这样做的，提出新做法时，另外的部门会觉得麻烦或风险高了，出现反对或供给想法的现象。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">这样的氛围让成员表达新想法时有顾虑，团队中的防御机制导致了无法突破。但一旦能看见，就可以决定要不要转变，团队常有隐性的惯性模式，也是按老套路做的原因。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\">&nbsp;</p>','2022-01-03 09:04:31','2022-01-04 13:35:42'),(30,'士气低落，不能面对困难和变化','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-right: 0.0000pt; margin-left: 21.0000pt; mso-para-margin-right: 0.0000gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0.0000gd; text-indent: -21.0000pt; mso-char-indent-count: 0.0000; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; mso-pagination: none; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\" align=\"justify\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">第一、发挥</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">目标意义感</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，帮助成员对目标有积极的看法</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解法参考：「</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">初心</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">价值创造</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、使命」等</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">第二、促进</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">积极</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的情绪</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">体验</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">从</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">过去</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的维度，有巅峰体验，能够自我欣赏有强信心；</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">从</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">未来</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的维度，逼真的想象等同于潜意识实现的未来，让团队抱有希望感。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-right: 0.0000pt; mso-para-margin-right: 0.0000gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0.0000gd; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; mso-pagination: none; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo2;\" align=\"justify\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;\">第三、</span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">链接底层的力量</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">回顾初心，为什么要做，同时从团队初心，链接到个人底层价值，包括我是谁的角色定位和追求的终极价值等，勇气就会激发出来，困难都会变小。</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\">当然需要教练提供专业的方式，带到相应的深度。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">更细节的解法，参考「士气」版块</span></span></p>','2022-01-03 09:35:24','2022-01-04 13:37:00'),(31,'各有各的想法，没法力往一处使','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">这个</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">问题有宽泛性，看各有想法的焦点是指目标，还是策略，还是在关系状态上。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">1、如果涉及到目标各有想法，需要审视利益相关者的不同视角，利益有没有共同的兼顾；</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">2、如果是涉及策略打法的各有想法，比如有路线之争论，思路不一样，这种情形很难处理，如果在高管层面，非常损耗。各有想法也有两面性，正向是指，避免团队完全一样，导致一头扎到坑里；但负向是指，带给团队有损耗，甚至有危机。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">3、如果没有到严重的程度，各有想法通常是在横线部门之间，具体做法可以参考「左右对齐」，管理者需要感受「不一致」的焦点在哪里，针对性的直面处理。如果良性的差异，没有影响任务进展，也可以观察发展态势。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">4、如果是指巨大的差异让大家隔阂和信任不足，通常要放下事情，先解决关系，解法参考「共同理解」和「信任」版块。</span></span></p>','2022-01-03 09:47:33','2022-01-04 13:25:03'),(32,'战斗力如何提升','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">激发战斗力，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">一般考虑四个方面。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">第一</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、奖励激励方式和力度</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">奖赏和回报分为内在的被关注和被认可、还有物质的金钱奖金等。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">检查要素：中早期物质回报少的情况下，有没有用充分用好内在回报？现在的奖励或者惩罚可以全部都列出来，看一看当时思考的意图和现在给团队激励的感受是否效果有达到、有无巨大的差距，是不是有调整？</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">第二、管理机制</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">要注意机制是管理业务流</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">精细化节点，而不是管理</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">任务计划层面的</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">细节</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">管控</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。比如说管控的是产出的质量，可以精细化。但是对</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">团队</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">执行的细节和步骤</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">不能精细化管理</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">否则</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">影响战斗力，因为被管控的感受会是让人抵抗，特别是业务前线的人，他们最了解前线的情况，需要灵活性。</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">过度微观化管理</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，往往是有负向作用的。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">第</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">三</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、文化层面</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">取决于业务形态需要什么样的文化去支持。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">比如说是年轻人或者是脑力工作者，他们更多的是需要一些参与度的、自主性的、灵活性的，激发他们的努力程度。管理者底层相不相信人是有自主性的。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解法可以参考：「年轻人共创」，通过共创的方式可以激发员工自主性，同时</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">兼顾</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">管理层的需要</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">第</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">四</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、能力部分</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">战斗力直接与执行的快慢有关系，也就团队的能力差距在哪里？优劣势在哪里，如何去优化？但是任何团队都需要有能力的多元性，需要有挑出一些关键的能力，然后识别哪些能力是可以培养的，哪些能力是不能培养，在选拔的时候必须具备的，这也是总部需要做的核心要点。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">解法可以参考：「能力盘点」、「角色分工」</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">另外，关于目标的意义感、价值感、认同感等来激发团队积极度，参考</span></span><span style=\"caret-color: #414750; color: #414750; font-family: Nunito, Montserrat, system-ui, BlinkMacSystemFont, -apple-system, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.1599999964237213px; background-color: #f8fafc;\"><a href=\"https://www.xteamengine.com/knowledge/33\">https://www.xteamengine.com/knowledge/33</a></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\">&nbsp;</p>','2022-01-03 11:27:59','2022-01-04 13:32:47'),(33,'努力不够、动力不足','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-right: 0.0000pt; mso-para-margin-right: 0.0000gd; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; mso-pagination: none; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo2;\" align=\"justify\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;\">1、影响要素之一：</span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">意义</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">感和认同感</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">对创业公司，未来发展可能性和创造价值的初心，都是最有感染力的部分，对于年轻的员工，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">更在意</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">价值感和参与感。所以，激发意义感和认同感，</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">对人的投入度有重大的影响</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">具体的解决思路参考「凝聚」版块，同时，向芯所有的研讨方式，都在群体沟通层面激发了参与感，参与感极大程度激发热情，并让成员对目标有承诺度和投入度。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">2、</span></span>影响要素之二：<span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">个体自带的</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">内驱力</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">比如内驱力足的人，就有内在动力特别要去做一些事情，比如成就驱动、价值驱动等。一方面，招人的时候，对内驱力有识别和重视；另一方面，管理者要识别他们的热情激发点，而不只停留在惯性的方式，比如潜意识认为只有物质奖励和惩罚监督才能督促执行。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-right: 0.0000pt; mso-para-margin-right: 0.0000gd; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; mso-pagination: none; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l2 level1 lfo3;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;\">3、</span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 14px;\">影响要素之三：</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\">奖励激励方式和力度</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">奖赏和回报分为内在的被关注和被认可、还有物质的金钱奖金等。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">检查要素：中早期物质回报少的情况下，有没有用充分用好内在回报？现在的奖励或者惩罚可以全部都列出来，看一看当时思考的意图和现在给团队激励的感受是否效果有达到、有无巨大的差距，是不是有调整？</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">总之，人的正向行为需要得到持续的反馈激励，投入度和努力度才会持续。识别业务特点，以及成员的特点，设置激发努力度的组合方式。激励也不是一层不变，要定期的感知效果和及时迭代。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">战斗力</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">提升，参考：</span></span><a href=\"https://www.xteamengine.com/knowledge/32\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\">https://www.xteamengine.com/knowledge/32</span></a></p>','2022-01-03 11:29:28','2022-01-04 13:21:12'),(34,'规模化复制的管理能力，需要注意什么？','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-right: 0.0000pt; margin-left: 21.0000pt; mso-para-margin-right: 0.0000gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0.0000gd; text-indent: -21.0000pt; mso-char-indent-count: 0.0000; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; mso-pagination: none; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">一、5种扩张的控制方式：</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">根据明茨伯格的总结，组织有</span>&nbsp;5&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">种典型的协调手段，分别是监督指令、结果标准化、流程标准化、技能标准化以及相互协调。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">1、监督指令是最强力的一种协调，其成本也相当高，因为需要非常多的管理者（经典组织理论强调管理幅度不超过&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">7&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">人，就是因为默认的协调手段就是监督指令）；</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">2、其次，为产出结果建立标准，使用标准来控制和验收，也能确保组织得到期待的成果；</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">3、如果无法使用直接监督和结果标准化，我们可以考虑将完成任务的过程予以标准化。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">4、假如上述三种手段都无法使用，我们还可以让执行任务的员工接受统一的训练和宣导，对其技能进行标准化。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">5、最后一项，是让完成任务的所有参与者相互协调。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">以</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">上是</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">控制</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">标准化从</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">强</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">到</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">弱拉出一条直线</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">二、规模化复制阶段，有三点注意：</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">1<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">管理</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">机制上</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">：远程沟通会议、区域</span>-<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">全国</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的报表等</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">结合</span>5<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">种控制方式设定；</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">2<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">运营</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">方式</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">：标准复制，</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">之前</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">指令协调可以处理，</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">但全国铺开需要</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">流程</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">和</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">技能标准化</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、人员培养等；</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">3<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、高管的</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">共识力：</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">这个阶段</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">分歧变多，决策速度和质量</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">要求变高</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">如果彼此不能深度沟通浮在表面，或者很多真实信息不会表达，团队的决策质量和认同度不够高，容易出现执行变形、执行慢等问题。</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">规模越大越脆弱</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，投后</span>6<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">年观察的数据，很多</span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">B</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">和</span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">C</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">轮遇到危机与这一点相关。</span></span></p>','2022-01-03 11:39:43','2022-01-03 11:39:43'),(35,'高管之间的关系，应该怎么去管理好？','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-right: 0.0000pt; margin-left: 21.0000pt; mso-para-margin-right: 0.0000gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0.0000gd; text-indent: -21.0000pt; mso-char-indent-count: 0.0000; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; mso-pagination: none; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\" align=\"justify\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Wingdings; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;\">&nbsp; </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">关系与</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">边界</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">角色</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">权威</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">等都有关系，</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">日常的关系处理，分为三个层面：</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">1<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、日常关系，最重要的是满足人的基本需求，</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">被尊重</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">被看见，</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">作为管理者</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">做到尊重，</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">并</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">看见人的独特性。</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">如果</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">权威高</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">一级的方式相处，成员对自主性的发挥没有影响，</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">也是</span>OK<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">2<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">工作关系，彼此</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">有</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">合作也有冲突，处理</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">分歧</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的时候，开诚不公，</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">以开放</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">建设性的心态，处理沟通上和合作上的难题。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">3<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">伙伴关系，</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">相处久的</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">团队</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">通常也有</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">私人关系，边界</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">会</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">模糊，融合</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">过度</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">也会带来边界不清烦扰，</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">私人关系也可以</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">保持适度的距离。</span></span></p>','2022-01-03 12:00:35','2022-01-03 12:00:35'),(36,'高管建的团建到底该怎么、做什么是有效的？','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-right: 0.0000pt; mso-para-margin-right: 0.0000gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0.0000gd; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; mso-pagination: none; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo2;\" align=\"justify\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;\">1、</span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">转化场景，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">才会有非正式的交流空间；</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-right: 0.0000pt; mso-para-margin-right: 0.0000gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0.0000gd; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; mso-pagination: none; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo2;\" align=\"justify\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;\">2、</span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">创造活动反思和</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">深度</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">对话</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的场，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">促进深层次的情感链接。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">注意：</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-right: 0.0000pt; mso-para-margin-right: 0.0000gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0.0000gd; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; mso-pagination: none; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l2 level1 lfo3;\" align=\"justify\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;\">1、</span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">方法</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">不能带出深度对话</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，或本身戒备</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">需要有专业的教练帮助，逐</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">渐打开内在状态打开，软化</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">关系的卡点</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，催化</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">对话的深度和质量。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">2<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、不要以</span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">CEO</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">要求的姿态组织，如果</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">觉得单边控制</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，可能有逆反和负向作用。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>','2022-01-03 12:01:15','2022-01-03 12:01:15'),(37,'为什么一群很厉害的人在一起总是产出很低效，很多内耗？','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">以下</span>3</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">部分值得思考</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">1<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">很厉害的个体，常常有独特性，个人贡献效能感非常好，而</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">在</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">团体环境，束缚</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">个体</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">马山</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">就可以感受到</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">但是感受到团队</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">帮助他</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">需要时间</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">磨合，</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">所以</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">个体</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">强</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的人，往往</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">觉得</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">团队拖慢节奏。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">2<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">团队合作</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">中</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">一定存在</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">差异化的看法，</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">就</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">有内部损耗</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">如果差异化</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">看法</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">没有高效</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">对话方式</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的刻意复盘和练习</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">沟通结果往往</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">创新性没有发生，时间损耗已经发生，效果不好，感觉</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">到一起</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">很低效。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">3<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">厉害个体</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的人</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，跟随方面比较弱，</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">且</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">主张多，彼此</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">容易产生</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">有竞争状态，不服谁，互相牵扯的局面。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">破局</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">方式</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">：</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">1<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、团队的领导结构，</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">发展</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">到</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">健康的局面；是指</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">事情决策都由什么方式进行的。比如分布式领导结构，是默认一些话题有不同人决策，大家彼此接受认同。但是不好的领导力的状态，体现在决策不服，不爽，不认同，自然影响执行和合作。一般有6种决策方式，可以让团队针对性的沟通对决策方式有共识。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">2<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">工作方式能兼顾集体合作和个人发挥的好处。</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">需要管理沟通阻碍点，和训练把差异观点带到深度</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">对话</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的团队技能，既能够</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">深层次的理解</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">彼此</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">又能</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">释放个体的潜力。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">3<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">Leader</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">是否能接受</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">个体层面</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">很强的人</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，合作</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">很</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">弱，</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">这样的团队状态有意识去管理，并引导团队重视和训练合作能力，以及挑选成员时，对合作能力的维度有评估。</span></span></p>','2022-01-03 12:02:52','2022-01-03 12:02:52'),(38,'如何让厉害的人凝聚在身边，更好地凝聚他们的心？','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;\">1、</span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">愿力越大，厉害的人为此</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">愿意</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">做贡献。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-right: 0.0000pt; mso-para-margin-right: 0.0000gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0.0000gd; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; mso-pagination: none; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo2;\" align=\"justify\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;\">2、</span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">特别</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">会</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">看见和挖掘</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">对方</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">优势</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，有</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">深层次的看见，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">对厉害的人</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">实现个人价值</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">和有</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">内在满足感。</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">并</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">营造机制和平台，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">让团队互相激发这一点。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">3<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、当然自己</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">也是很厉害的人</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，有品格和个人魅力愿意被跟随。</span></span></p>','2022-01-03 12:03:18','2022-01-03 12:03:18'),(39,'人效提升，从哪些要点着手？','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">1、首先降本，这一点不是直接指向砍人，可以先定义</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">核心人才，哪些人价值创造</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">是</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">最大</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">识别出来。其他价值创造的环节，</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">哪些替代性高，可以</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">用</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">更</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">低成本</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">方式满足。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">2、其次增产，通常想到的是盯执行过程，这种方式底层是相信人需要管控。但是如果业务特点偏创新和员工对自主性的需求较高，从</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">内部运作方面，尽量以减少束缚，而非增加监督的方式，营造高自主性的工作环境。</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">让员工</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">工作和生活更能够兼顾</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，这些都可以提高人的产出。特别对于</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">脑力活动</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">者</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，在</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">偏向于</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">成就感</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">工作环境中，工作效率会更高。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">到底是监督管控还是激发自主，</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">人是复杂和可塑的，</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">有效的结合起来提高产出。</span></span></p>','2022-01-03 12:44:05','2022-01-04 13:22:23'),(40,'砍人之后，要注意什么？','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">事关三分以上人员调整会有非常大的影响。如果有这个动作，一定要把后面的管理动作和大家说清楚，让大家对后面有新的准备，不会让猜疑各种情绪肆意飘散。相当于是一个团队在造的过程。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">最重要的是要了解留下来的人考虑的是什么。</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">留下来的「</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">我们</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">」</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">一起要去做什么，必须要达到实现什么，给大家吃一个定心丸</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">这个时候最重要的是让情绪的感受能呈现出来</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">这些情绪和能量就是低谷期最大的抵抗力，可以通过消极抵抗的方式展现。需要一个包容和接纳的环境，给它释放负能量的。你说未来怎么可以赢？很多人是没有心思去</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">想</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，大家停留在当下的情绪要释放出来，需要一点时间</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">才能再去</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">一起看未来。</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">让</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">他们感知到自己是被接纳的，愿意听他们的</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">声音</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">总结三</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">个方向</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">第一，宣讲明确</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">未来的</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">方向</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">；</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">第二</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">要释放情绪，双向沟通</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">让负面情绪有</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">疏通和释放；第三，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">管理者要去感知团队现在目前在</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">关注</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">什么，重点是有情绪，需要接纳的关怀</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">？</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">还是未来怎么走</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">比较迷惘，</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">需要</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">探索未来</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">？</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">重要的去感知团队，而不是在于思考用什么样的具体方式去调整</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">感知这个场域</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">需要的重点在哪里</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。</span></span></p>','2022-01-03 12:46:45','2022-01-03 12:46:45'),(41,'管理层如何获得好的激励？','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">向芯</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">引擎具体不聚焦于机制方面的服务咨询</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，简要回答供参考。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">激励</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">需要结合公司的战略规划、财务目标、未来关键指标，然后定流多少池子来做激励。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">贡献的程度到底在哪里？</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">人才激励的水准参照</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">什么市场的数据？</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">都需要考虑。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">高管人才</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">注意激励的长期是薪水的匹配，重要要看</span>&nbsp;package&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，包括</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">月薪、绩效、年度股权。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">「</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">年度的绩效</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">奖励」</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">是中早期</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">最重要的部分，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">留多少池子做奖励</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">公司的目标和个人的目标</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">如何</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">联合</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">？</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">如果公司没完成，个人完成好奖励是什么？如果公司完成目标，但个人绩效一般奖励又是什么？各种情形都要定一个水位线和参考的重要维度。</span></span></p>','2022-01-03 12:49:54','2022-01-03 12:49:54'),(42,'年轻员工的文化怎么打造？','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-right: 0.0000pt; mso-para-margin-right: 0.0000gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0.0000gd; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; mso-pagination: none; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo2;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;\">年轻人的在意点：</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-right: 0.0000pt; mso-para-margin-right: 0.0000gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0.0000gd; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; mso-pagination: none; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo2;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;\">1、</span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">在乎工作赋予的意义感、社会认可度是主要诉求。可以聊聊工作意味着什么？为什么？加入眼前的工作对他什么意义？现在公司有什么想要的，他有什么建议是可以回馈到这个公司的。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-right: 0.0000pt; mso-para-margin-right: 0.0000gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0.0000gd; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; mso-pagination: none; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo2;\" align=\"justify\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;\">2、</span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">希望</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">有自己的空间，不被人主宰，不为</span>&nbsp;KPI&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">做事。可以参考我们参与感和价值感的一些共创会的部分。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-right: 0.0000pt; mso-para-margin-right: 0.0000gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0.0000gd; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; mso-pagination: none; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo2;\" align=\"justify\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;\">3、</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">他们的危机感很少</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，大部分</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">可以接受左一点或者右一点，只要给出比较有空间的被尊重的感觉，让他们感觉公司为他们着想，只要是一种感性的喜欢就会有力量。</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">这种环境是可以营造出来的，员工很喜欢这里的感觉，我喜欢你就会挺你支持你。文化，就是大部分员工幸福跟认同的人，留下不认同的人就走开。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">关于自主性的管理，可以参考解法「年轻人文化」</span></span></p>','2022-01-03 12:53:04','2022-01-03 12:53:04'),(43,'如何做员工的汰换？','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">开除之前反馈具体的要求</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">注意反馈的双方约定一定要强调，犯的错误已经危及到这个人</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">「</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">留用</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">」</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的问题要提出来，这个约定也需要足够的清晰并且有记录</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">比如说你做不到什么时候就涉及到开除，可以称之为</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">「</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">改进协议</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">」。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">有柔性的空间被</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">提前</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">告知，也不会有</span>&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">Surprise<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，最后</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">达不到标准，公司的政策是允许转岗还是必须离开。这样让团员工知晓</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，也</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">约定了共识，觉得公平。如果在不知情的情况下不知道标准，</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">员</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">工会有很大的</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">反</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">弹和情绪</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，影响</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">人事的风险</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">和</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">公司文化。</span></span></p>','2022-01-03 12:54:25','2022-01-03 12:54:25'),(44,'l如何提高高管战略思考能力和理解WHY的能力？','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">不是</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">靠</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">单次培训</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">能解决这个</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">问题，是持续互动沟通的辅导，有足够多的时间经常一起讨论战略问题，</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">Leader</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">掌握的咨询和考虑</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的推理可以有效</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">传递，互动中培养这个能力。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">一般</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">7-9</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">人的</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">核心</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">是</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">第一层，多人数辅导</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">难度变大</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">如果涉及到</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">团队更大的范围，提升</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">团队</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">沟通的质量，团队研讨的方式</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">具体参考「</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">目标对齐</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">」。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">通过双向沟通的参与度激活，以及传递推理的细节过程，起到三</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">重效果，</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">让员工学习和</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">模仿思考过程，知道更多</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">真实信息，用参与感提升认同度。</span></span></p>','2022-01-03 12:58:01','2022-01-03 12:58:01'),(45,'远程办公协同的团队，如何促进凝聚和协同关系？','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">1、创造非正式的沟通场合</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，因为在一起办公，可以有</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">物理空间</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">走动</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，比如</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">茶水间</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">等遇到后的</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">闲聊，可以创造场域时空的相遇</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">了解彼此工作生活等</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。所以定期组织非正式的关系链接的沟通场景。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">2、正式会议</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">前的</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">check in/check out</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，比如开头分享每个人当下的状态和期待，最近关注的和想突破的事情等。比如结尾可以一句话总结收获、心情、或表达最某位同事的感谢或认可等。</span></span></p>','2022-01-03 13:01:31','2022-01-03 13:01:31'),(46,'会议效率总是比较低，跑偏了，开会没有结果，感觉大家讨论的质量也有限，最后不得不自己拍板来结束会议。','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">1<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">过程管理：总体节奏的把握，时间、发散、主题发散，适度提炼总结，评估不同看法的，收敛共识的观点。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">2<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">提前设立会议的议题的主题、议程</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">和时间安排、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">产出目标。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">3<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">增加议题的控制人。适当的时候提醒大家回到会议初中的议题上，允许有人把大家拉回来。当团队出现分歧情绪、发散争论等等阻碍效率的地方，可以暂停，要求大家给大家提问，你们目前争论是跟议题的关系是什么？是有关还是无关？想说的重点是什么？想让大家知道的是什么，然后引导大家回到正题。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">4<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">会议形式上也需要关手机、关电脑</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">5<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">参与人要合适，不能无关议题的人都在，</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">不积极</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">参与投入度会影响大部分人。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">6<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">对话质量，安全感的氛围</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">帮助成员积极发表观点，及承载差异性的互动。</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">大家愿不愿意表达真实想法？在这里愿不愿意表达观点，愿不愿意积极地贡献想法？这背后所有的都与团队的氛围有关系，防备不安全，不敢说，说了也没</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">或者是说了之后引起别人攻击，或侵犯了别人的利益等等，但凡这样的不安全感的氛围和环境，直接影响了沟通质量。</span></span></p>','2022-01-03 13:05:00','2022-01-03 13:05:00'),(47,'想以人为本，重视人的发展，从哪几个方面着手去做？','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">首先，</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">内心</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">理念，</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">是真心这样做，</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">还是控制人的目的。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">如果是</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">内心理念，做到什么</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">取决于多大的能力。比如</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">基本尊重，不攻击人</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">是最基础的</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。创造多一点机会，提升他们生活品质和兼顾家庭</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的空间</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">；工作中，给予培训和机会历练</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">等</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">同时不求回报的去实践这些理念。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">如果是手法，</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">为了</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">生产效率变高，</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">是一种</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">工具化，员工</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">也会</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">感受到</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">是</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">交换交易，关心关怀</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">会</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">变质了。</span></span></p>','2022-01-03 13:05:54','2022-01-03 13:05:54'),(48,'团队间配合有冲突的情况，如何判断是优先共识角色 还是策略？','<p>如果感知到策略是主要的矛盾，然后角色相对清晰和明确的，讨论策略优先；</p>\r\n<p>如果说大家对策略比较认可，角色边界模糊，让策略执行摩擦力大，肯定角色摆在前面处理。</p>\r\n<p>主要是感知所在的情景，做选择的一个过程。</p>','2022-01-05 03:06:27','2022-01-05 03:06:27'),(49,'战略共识会的沟通要点','<p style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; color: #464646; font-family: 宋体; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: #c80000; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">战略共识会的痛点</strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; color: #464646; font-family: 宋体; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; color: #464646; font-family: 宋体; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">每年到了第四季度，很多企业都会开战略研讨会。但很多高管战略会其实不算是一个真正的对话，其中容易犯的两种错误是：</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; color: #464646; font-family: 宋体; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<blockquote class=\"\" style=\"margin: 1em 0px; padding: 4px 0px 0px 10px; outline: 0px; border-left-width: 3px; border-left-color: #dbdbdb; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5); font-size: 15px; max-width: 100%; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei UI\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\" data-type=\"2\" data-url=\"\" data-author-name=\"\" data-content-utf8-length=\"65\" data-source-title=\"\">\r\n<section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n<section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; color: #464646; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">第一种，决而不议。会议并不真正讨论，走一个形式，等于是宣告一个决定；</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; color: #464646; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; color: #464646; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">第二种，议而不决。讨论后没有结论，没有与实际的行动相连接。</span></p>\r\n</section>\r\n</section>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; color: #464646; font-family: 宋体; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; color: #464646; font-family: 宋体; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">这样的战略会议，效果是可想而知的。即使中间有对话，对话的质量其实都不会高的。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; color: #464646; font-family: 宋体; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; color: #464646; font-family: 宋体; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">而且这种低质量沟通，跟与会者的沟通技巧是无关的，整个会议的设置和一些隐性的规则，就几乎决定了质量的低下。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; color: #464646; font-family: 宋体; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; color: #464646; font-family: 宋体; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">如果组织能够举办一些真正做到开放、平等的会议，来探讨战略话题，那我们就迈开了真正重要的一步。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; color: #464646; font-family: 宋体; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; color: #464646; font-family: 宋体; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">但这不表示困难就没有了，</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: #c80000; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">战略会议其中一个难题就是处理彼此之间的差异或分歧。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; color: #464646; font-family: 宋体; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: #c80000; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"font-size: 8pt;\">具体方法请到文章结尾，扫码小程序查看「分歧解决」实操方案。</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; color: #464646; font-family: 宋体; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; color: #464646; font-family: 宋体; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">当外部形势变化，而业务也有很多方向可以去探索和尝试时，产生分歧的可能性就会比较大。主持会议的人，能够敏锐识别不同人背后的出发点或他们所理解的方向，才能促进高层领导者开好战略共识会。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; color: #464646; font-family: 宋体; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; color: #464646; font-family: 宋体; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">也只有达成了真正的共识，才能在高层团队中凝心聚力，展现出一种明确性，使得方向明确，行动有力。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; color: #464646; font-family: 宋体; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; color: #464646; font-family: 宋体; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">战略共识达成过程中的对话，与人的心智模式是高度相关的。越是重要的议题，往往复杂度也越高，观点和推理过程也会越多样。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; color: #464646; font-family: 宋体; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; color: #464646; font-family: 宋体; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">这个时候的多样性和分歧，其实很难用简单的所谓正确或者错误的两分思维来处理观点分歧，必须要回到各种观点之争背后的基本假设和推导过程，才有可能将对话带入到比较深刻的层面。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; color: #464646; font-family: 宋体; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; color: #464646; font-family: 宋体; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">因此，要想谈话有质量，我们需要建立良好的氛围，鼓励彼此进行探询，才能让对话从表面的内容切入，逐渐深入到推理过程以及基本假设，进而触及每个高管的心智模式，带来深刻的对话，高质量的决策，和对自己的深刻反思。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; color: #464646; font-family: 宋体; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; color: #464646; font-family: 宋体; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: #c80000; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">2.心智模式工具&mdash;&mdash;推论阶梯</strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; color: #464646; font-family: 宋体; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; color: #464646; font-family: 宋体; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">战略共识需要可以敞开心扉的开放氛围，大家可以深入到心智模式的层次，去检视基本逻辑和假设，回到原点，去探询这些基本假设对我们观点的影响。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; color: #464646; font-family: 宋体; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; color: #464646; font-family: 宋体; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; color: #c80000; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">在观点层面无法达成一致时，深入到基本假设的层次去探询彼此的差异，</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">是一个可能的出路，让我们在包容差异的同时，保持着对话的前进。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; caret-color: #333333; color: #333333; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei UI\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; color: #464646; font-family: 宋体; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; color: #464646; font-family: 宋体; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">做到这个，我们才能让对话在更深入的层面继续进行，之后所呈现的共识，才能让战略的共识有质量、有品质，而不是表面的共识。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; color: #464646; font-family: 宋体; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; color: #464646; font-family: 宋体; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">每个人都会基于看到的事实、资讯，产生不同的理解。用推论阶梯可以很好地理解其背后的推导过程。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; color: #464646; font-family: 宋体; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; color: #464646; font-family: 宋体; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">从所有的可被观察的原始数据出发，按推论阶梯一般有以下步骤：</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; color: #464646; font-family: 宋体; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<blockquote class=\"\" style=\"margin: 1em 0px; padding: 4px 0px 0px 10px; outline: 0px; border-left-width: 3px; border-left-color: #dbdbdb; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5); font-size: 15px; max-width: 100%; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei UI\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\" data-type=\"2\" data-url=\"\" data-author-name=\"\" data-content-utf8-length=\"90\" data-source-title=\"\">\r\n<section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n<section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; color: #464646; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">第一阶梯，选择数据，不同人看到的焦点不一样，他们从原始数据中所选择的数据也不一样；</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; color: #464646; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; color: #464646; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">第二阶梯，不同人会对数据赋予不同的含义；</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; color: #464646; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; color: #464646; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">第三阶梯，基于所赋予的含义，每个人做出不同的回应和行动。</span></p>\r\n</section>\r\n</section>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; color: #464646; font-family: 宋体; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; color: #464646; font-family: 宋体; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">例如，在做战略研讨时，有人也许先抛出一个观点&mdash;&mdash;这个业务应该做to B,不是to C。这样的观点已经走完阶梯了。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; color: #464646; font-family: 宋体; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; color: #464646; font-family: 宋体; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">当他有了这样的观点</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; color: #888888; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">（结论）</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">时，实际他可能从原始数据挑选了部分内容&mdash;&mdash;对to B业务相关的资讯更关注，对to C业务方面的资讯视而不见。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; color: #464646; font-family: 宋体; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; color: #464646; font-family: 宋体; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">当他把这些信息赋予一个含义</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; color: #888888; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">（例如：to B业务机会更多）</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">时，就有了自己的观点和立场；接下来，他选择抛出这个观点，就变成了一个行动。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; color: #464646; font-family: 宋体; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; color: #464646; font-family: 宋体; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; color: #c80000; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">每个人的心智模式不一样，他的滤镜不一样，他看到的东西就会有区别。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; color: #464646; font-family: 宋体; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; color: #464646; font-family: 宋体; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">所以，在做战略共识时，因为心智结构不一致，挑选数据的方式不一致，他们的观点就会不一样。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; color: #464646; font-family: 宋体; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; color: #464646; font-family: 宋体; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">这时候，不能用简单的对错来对待观点，需要大家一起看到整体的画面，一起深度交流，拓展彼此的视角，才能让这个对话过程变得更加丰富，而决策的质量也因此更高。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; color: #464646; font-family: 宋体; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; color: #464646; font-family: 宋体; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: #c80000; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">3.避免单边控制模式</strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; color: #464646; font-family: 宋体; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; color: #464646; font-family: 宋体; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">沟通中，如果不把结论所隐含的背景、假设条件展现出来就急着下结论，往往会陷入激烈的争论或者争吵中。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; color: #464646; font-family: 宋体; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; color: #464646; font-family: 宋体; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">当有人评判别人的观点是错的，或者是观点不完整时，其实引发了对话中的张力，让彼此变成了进攻防守的关系。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; color: #464646; font-family: 宋体; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; color: #464646; font-family: 宋体; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">只关注自己赢，不要输，总是认为只有自己对，掩盖负面的感受，显得理性，这种心智模式被称为单边控制模式。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; color: #464646; font-family: 宋体; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; color: #464646; font-family: 宋体; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; color: #c80000; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">在单边控制模式下，双方就会把对话视为输赢的关系。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">同时，如果觉得对方不太礼貌，也会把话藏在心里不说，这样的对话非常不透明，严重影响了对话质量。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; caret-color: #333333; color: #333333; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei UI\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"caret-color: #c80000; color: #c80000; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.666666984558105px; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff;\">具体方法请到文章结尾，扫码小程序查看「目标共振」等实操方案。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; color: #464646; font-family: 宋体; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; color: #464646; font-family: 宋体; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">而在碰到类似重要的战略问题的时候，也会让对话变得低效，讨论并不充分，质量低下。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; color: #464646; font-family: 宋体; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; color: #464646; font-family: 宋体; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">这样，谈话内容很可能停留在观点层面，缺乏事实支撑，或者过快跳入结论但缺乏推导过程的显性化。当别人不清楚其观点推导过程时，往往又变成观点层面的互相争执。这也是很多CEO觉得战略共识会效果不大的原因。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; color: #464646; font-family: 宋体; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; color: #464646; font-family: 宋体; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">战略其实没有绝对的对错。为什么要讨论战略？是为了找到那个画面，找到它的来龙去脉，这就会让我们看得更清楚，甚至到最后实施的时候都是清楚的。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; color: #464646; font-family: 宋体; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; color: #464646; font-family: 宋体; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">其实战略也并非要面面俱到，因为很多市场信息不在掌控之内，也没有更多领域的专家给予信息的反馈。但恰恰是在讨论时，可以让大家看到更多的信息和可能。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; color: #464646; font-family: 宋体; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; color: #464646; font-family: 宋体; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">在讨论中也会经常被打断，但往往是批判对方的观点或方向，而很少有人会去问：&ldquo;你为什么认为是这个方向，你是怎么得出这个方向的？&rdquo;久而久之，很少会有人再提建议了。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; color: #464646; font-family: 宋体; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; color: #464646; font-family: 宋体; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: #c80000; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">4.战略对话的综合视角</strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; color: #464646; font-family: 宋体; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; color: #464646; font-family: 宋体; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">战略是深思熟虑还是机缘巧合，这是两种不同的观点和视角：</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; color: #464646; font-family: 宋体; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<blockquote class=\"\" style=\"margin: 1em 0px; padding: 4px 0px 0px 10px; outline: 0px; border-left-width: 3px; border-left-color: #dbdbdb; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5); font-size: 15px; max-width: 100%; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei UI\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\" data-type=\"2\" data-url=\"\" data-author-name=\"\" data-content-utf8-length=\"66\" data-source-title=\"\">\r\n<section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n<section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; color: #464646; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">其一，从规划视角，通过充分讨论，探寻事情本质，达成共识，做规划来推动战略的实现；</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; color: #464646; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; color: #464646; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">其二，业务前线的人在打仗过程中提炼出有效的战略打法。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; color: #464646; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; color: #464646; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"caret-color: #c80000; color: #c80000; font-size: 10.666666984558105px;\">具体方法请到文章结尾，扫码小程序查看「目标共创」「洞察信号」「槽点改进」等实操方案。</span></span></p>\r\n</section>\r\n</section>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; color: #464646; font-family: 宋体; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; color: #464646; font-family: 宋体; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">这两种视角都是有价值的，只有两者结合才是战略对话的综合视角。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; color: #464646; font-family: 宋体; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; color: #464646; font-family: 宋体; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">战略决策要达成共识，需要有足够安全的心理氛围，让高管们探询不同观点背后的基本假设，以及彼此的心智模式。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; color: #464646; font-family: 宋体; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; color: #464646; font-family: 宋体; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">战略共识是让大家看到整体画面的过程，必须要深度交流，不能是单向交流或表达，这样大家得到的信息会越来越丰富，参与者也会越来越愿意开会，未来也会留意这些信息。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; color: #464646; font-family: 宋体; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; color: #464646; font-family: 宋体; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">战略对话的会议是非常有难度的，不是所有人都有开放度来探讨。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; color: #464646; font-family: 宋体; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; color: #464646; font-family: 宋体; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">如果CEO有足够的开放度，作为管理者要珍惜这个机会，因为你们共同影响了公司的未来，公司的成功都掌握在你们这一群人手中，这时的对话质量会直接影响到将来战略落地的效果。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; color: #464646; font-family: 宋体; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; color: #464646; font-family: 宋体; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img src=\"http://xin-engine.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/tinymce/images/7e784c9eb3dd19f985ebb397a4a59eb161de502cc2a3e.jpeg\" alt=\"\" /></span></p>','2022-01-12 03:27:32','2022-01-12 03:51:16'),(50,'团队中反复出现的沟通问题，怎么破？','<p>Q： 团队中如果反复出现的沟通问题，怎么破？</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>情景举例：</p>\r\n<p>团队有戒备或者回避冲突、沟通氛围差、互相推诿等</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>一、看见模式：</p>\r\n<p>问题重复出现，很难改变，很有可能存在僵化的互动方式，这种互动方式低效且无效，并且大家体验都不好，重复的让任务卡顿，而且大部分人都能感知到，但很难看清楚背后的因果关系，容易困在里面。如果遇到这样的情况，管理者需要了解一个词就是互动模式。</p>\r\n<p>互动模式是指反复出现这类问题的源头，存在于团队成员之间的人际互动当中。比如说当出现不同声音的时候，某些成员会跳出来让大家尽快形成一致，不要浪费时间。团队潜意识会认为差异化的表达是和效率相违背的，这就是一种模式。但每个团队的模式都不一样。</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>二、怎么解决</p>\r\n<p>做法就是在团队日常的沟通讨论中，让外部专业的老师去观察大家的互动模式，把这种盲点和隐形的互动源头显性化出来。</p>\r\n<p>共同看见「互动的固定方式」对大家的影响，并形成行动计划和团队的行为约束。直击问题重复的源头，并针对性的共同行动，这是最高效最有效的方式，</p>\r\n<p>通常破除这种互动模式的有两种做法：</p>\r\n<p>第一种，在重大会议的时候，通过的氛围场域的营造，以及在流程上的设计，帮助这种模式不出现，提升会议的参与度和共识度，是短期作用。</p>\r\n<p>第二种，长期的行为改变，需要有共同意愿的开启，以及一定时间的刻意约束和管理。</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>三、常见误区：</p>\r\n<p>这类问题，通过提高个体的沟通能力，效果不达预期。</p>\r\n<p>团队互动的质量和效率，最有关的要素是沟通氛围（单场会议可以通过场域营造和流程设计改变、长期有效需破掉重复出现的问题源头）</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>四、原理</p>\r\n<p>人际互动有复杂性，问题是相互间影响塑造而成的，解决也要回到塑造而成的隐含的模式中。</p>','2022-01-12 03:40:10','2022-01-12 03:40:10');
